  <body region="amara-subtitle-area">
    <div>
      <p end="00:00:27,978" begin="00:00:23,974">- [Colin Beavan] Vi pr&#248;ver &#229; leve i en by uten &#229; p&#229;virke milj&#248;et-</p>
      <p end="00:00:30,536" begin="00:00:27,978">-og jeg skriver om <span tts:fontStyle="italic">NoImpactMan.com.</span></p>
      <p end="00:00:41,658" begin="00:00:37,028">Vi feller altfor mange tr&#230;r. Vi trenger de for &#229; redde planeten.</p>
      <p end="00:00:45,191" begin="00:00:43,160">Og isbj&#248;rnene.</p>
      <p end="00:00:50,496" begin="00:00:46,580">Jeg pr&#248;ver &#229; leve et liv som er i tr&#229;d med mine verdier.</p>
      <p end="00:00:54,129" begin="00:00:52,377">[Sukk] Faen!</p>
      <p end="00:01:07,934" begin="00:00:54,129">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="00:01:10,604" begin="00:01:07,934">- [TV-vert] Folk har et &#248;nske om &#229; erstatte den amerikanske m&#229;ten-</p>
      <p end="00:01:13,273" begin="00:01:10,604">-med vindkraft og barkeburgere.</p>
      <p end="00:01:14,441" begin="00:01:13,273">[Publikum ler]</p>
      <p end="00:01:17,402" begin="00:01:14,441">Denne familien fra New York, Beavan-familien, er fem m&#229;neder-</p>
      <p end="00:01:20,655" begin="00:01:17,402">-p&#229; vei i et &#229;r langt oppdrag for &#229; leve uten &#229; p&#229;virke milj&#248;et.</p>
      <p end="00:01:24,326" begin="00:01:20,655">Reglene er: Ingen toalettpapir, lysp&#230;rer-</p>
      <p end="00:01:27,579" begin="00:01:24,326">-barberblad, blader, aviser-</p>
      <p end="00:01:31,541" begin="00:01:27,579">-TV, fly, tog, biler, heiser, plastikkposer-</p>
      <p end="00:01:34,377" begin="00:01:31,541">-eller innkj&#248;p av noe nytt.</p>
      <p end="00:01:37,088" begin="00:01:34,377">De forgifter v&#229;rt samfunn, og her i studio for &#229; forsvare seg selv-</p>
      <p end="00:01:40,634" begin="00:01:37,088">-er patriarken for disse eco-Mansonene, Colin Beavan.</p>
      <p end="00:01:42,014" begin="00:01:40,634">Mr. Beavan, takk for at du kom hit.</p>
      <p end="00:01:44,346" begin="00:01:42,014">[Publikum klapper og jubler]</p>
      <p end="00:01:49,267" begin="00:01:44,346">- Med oss har vi forfatter og "No Impact Man", Colin Beavan.</p>
      <p end="00:01:53,319" begin="00:01:49,267">- Vi starter i kveld med en mann, hans familie og et radikalt eksperiment-</p>
      <p end="00:01:54,773" begin="00:01:53,319">-for &#229; hjelpe planeten.</p>
      <p end="00:01:56,359" begin="00:01:54,773">Med mer enn 40 % av samfunnet-</p>
      <p end="00:01:59,681" begin="00:01:56,359">-som er overbevist om at mennesker for&#229;rsaker global oppvarming.</p>
      <p end="00:02:01,610" begin="00:01:59,681">- [Colin] Jeg tenkte at hva om jeg faktisk pr&#248;vde-</p>
      <p end="00:02:03,725" begin="00:02:01,610">-&#229; ikke skade milj&#248;et?</p>
      <p end="00:02:06,117" begin="00:02:03,725">Hva ville det f&#248;les som?</p>
      <p end="00:02:08,700" begin="00:02:06,117">Er det mulig? Er det praktisk?</p>
      <p end="00:02:12,535" begin="00:02:08,700">[Fly tar av]</p>
      <p end="00:02:32,143" begin="00:02:16,044">[Bilst&#248;y]</p>
      <p end="00:02:35,355" begin="00:02:32,143">- En av de tingene jeg, som forfatter, har hatt lyst til-</p>
      <p end="00:02:37,274" begin="00:02:35,355">-fordi mine to siste b&#248;ker har v&#230;rt historieb&#248;ker-</p>
      <p end="00:02:40,443" begin="00:02:37,274">-er &#229; bli en aktivistforfatter.</p>
      <p end="00:02:42,988" begin="00:02:40,443">P&#229; en ydmyk m&#229;te, &#248;nsker jeg at-</p>
      <p end="00:02:46,867" begin="00:02:42,988">-mitt forfatterskap hjelper verden.</p>
      <p end="00:02:49,035" begin="00:02:46,867">For et &#229;r skal min kone, min datter og jeg-</p>
      <p end="00:02:50,494" begin="00:02:49,035">-mens vi lever midt i New York City-</p>
      <p end="00:02:52,064" begin="00:02:50,494">-fors&#248;ke og leve uten &#229;-</p>
      <p end="00:02:54,510" begin="00:02:52,064">-p&#229;virke milj&#248;et.</p>
      <p end="00:02:58,503" begin="00:02:54,510">Dette betyr at vi ikke skaper s&#248;ppel, eller noe hurtigmat-</p>
      <p end="00:03:01,506" begin="00:02:58,503">-eller slipper ut karbondioksid; s&#229; det blir ikke noe kj&#248;ring eller flyging-</p>
      <p end="00:03:04,259" begin="00:03:01,506">-ingen uthelling av gifter i vannet; s&#229; ikke vaskemiddel-</p>
      <p end="00:03:08,973" begin="00:03:04,259">-ikke kj&#248;p av produkter fra fjerne land; s&#229; ingen frukt fra New Zealand.</p>
      <p end="00:03:12,017" begin="00:03:08,973">Og for ikke &#229; nevne, ingen heiser, ingen undergrunnsbaner-</p>
      <p end="00:03:15,145" begin="00:03:12,017">-ingen produkter i emballasje, ingen plastikk, ingen AC, ingen TV eller papir.</p>
      <p end="00:03:16,605" begin="00:03:15,145">Og s&#229; videre.</p>
      <p end="00:03:20,901" begin="00:03:16,605">Det er et sammendrag av prosjektet.</p>
      <p end="00:03:23,194" begin="00:03:20,901">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="00:03:34,549" begin="00:03:23,194">[Gatest&#248;y]</p>
      <p end="00:03:39,294" begin="00:03:36,086">- [Michelle Conlin] Colin fortalte meg hva vi skulle gj&#248;re-</p>
      <p end="00:03:44,341" begin="00:03:39,294">-og hvordan reagerte jeg? Jeg var opphisset for at han hadde en id&#233;-</p>
      <p end="00:03:46,802" begin="00:03:44,341">-han var opphisset for.</p>
      <p end="00:03:50,138" begin="00:03:46,802">Det var det viktigste.</p>
      <p end="00:03:51,464" begin="00:03:50,138">Siden vi gj&#248;r alt dette-</p>
      <p end="00:03:53,366" begin="00:03:51,464">-s&#229; hvorfor tar vi ikke med mine to avhengigheter samtidig-</p>
      <p end="00:03:56,982" begin="00:03:53,366">-som er shopping og reality-TV?</p>
      <p end="00:04:02,067" begin="00:03:57,938">Jeg er glad i reality-TV, og er avhengig og ekspert p&#229; det.</p>
      <p end="00:04:03,693" begin="00:04:02,067">- Se p&#229; ansiktet hennes akkurat n&#229;.</p>
      <p end="00:04:04,861" begin="00:04:03,693">[Latter]</p>
      <p end="00:04:09,157" begin="00:04:04,861">Det ser ut som hun blir revet med.</p>
      <p end="00:04:11,117" begin="00:04:09,157">- Det er bra.</p>
      <p end="00:04:14,746" begin="00:04:11,117">Jeg har hatt et intenst forhold til kleskj&#248;p.</p>
      <p end="00:04:16,957" begin="00:04:14,746">Catherine Malandrino eksempelsalg.</p>
      <p end="00:04:20,168" begin="00:04:16,957">Jean Paul Gaultier er s&#229; morsom og jeg ser deg ved midnatt-</p>
      <p end="00:04:22,337" begin="00:04:20,168">-og s&#229; har vi middag klokken 2 p&#229; natten.</p>
      <p end="00:04:23,880" begin="00:04:22,337">Marc Jacobs er mer som:</p>
      <p end="00:04:28,598" begin="00:04:23,880">"Jeg er gift og mor, men jeg pr&#248;ver &#229; trene litt."</p>
      <p end="00:04:31,599" begin="00:04:28,613">Jeg er avhengig av fruktose, sirup-</p>
      <p end="00:04:36,810" begin="00:04:31,599">-TV og spiser kj&#248;tt.</p>
      <p end="00:04:39,773" begin="00:04:36,810">Jeg var ingen milj&#248;forkjemper.</p>
      <p end="00:04:42,732" begin="00:04:39,773">Jeg var den typiske forbrukeren...</p>
      <p end="00:04:44,985" begin="00:04:42,732">Jeg er en forbruker.</p>
      <p end="00:04:47,713" begin="00:04:44,985">Jeg er hurtigmat-junkie.</p>
      <p end="00:04:51,008" begin="00:04:49,236">- Du ble redd fordi du ikke var i stand-</p>
      <p end="00:04:52,343" begin="00:04:51,008">-til &#229; forbruke ting i et &#229;r.</p>
      <p end="00:04:54,058" begin="00:04:52,343">- Ja det var jeg.</p>
      <p end="00:04:55,662" begin="00:04:54,074">- S&#229; du pr&#248;ver &#229; forbruke et &#229;rs forbruk i l&#248;pet av en uke.</p>
      <p end="00:04:58,331" begin="00:04:55,662">- Jeg droppet l&#248;nnsslippen.</p>
      <p end="00:05:00,291" begin="00:04:58,331">Chloe-st&#248;vler; det kostet mye.</p>
      <p end="00:05:01,334" begin="00:05:00,291">- Hvor mye?</p>
      <p end="00:05:03,128" begin="00:05:01,334">- P&#229; en m&#229;te s&#229; er jeg forskrekket av meg selv.</p>
      <p end="00:05:04,504" begin="00:05:03,128">- Kan du si hvor mye?</p>
      <p end="00:05:07,674" begin="00:05:04,504">- Dette er s&#229; fryktelig.</p>
      <p end="00:05:09,968" begin="00:05:07,674">Jeg skjemmes av meg selv.</p>
      <p end="00:05:13,221" begin="00:05:09,968">[Colin ler]</p>
      <p end="00:05:14,973" begin="00:05:13,221">Dette var det siste rushet.</p>
      <p end="00:05:16,224" begin="00:05:14,973">- Ja, dette var rangelen. Jeg skj&#248;nner.</p>
      <p end="00:05:17,684" begin="00:05:16,224">- Ja! Dette er regninga til rangelen.</p>
      <p end="00:05:20,495" begin="00:05:17,684">- Jeg lo fordi jeg var bare ute etter n&#248;dvendige ting.</p>
      <p end="00:05:22,368" begin="00:05:20,538">- Det var som at du aldri hadde gjort det f&#248;r.</p>
      <p end="00:05:23,481" begin="00:05:22,647">- Okey.</p>
      <p end="00:05:28,445" begin="00:05:23,481">- Jeg brukte penger p&#229; t&#229;pelige ting.</p>
      <p end="00:05:29,946" begin="00:05:28,445">- Jeg bryr meg ikke om hvor mye du bruker.</p>
      <p end="00:05:32,741" begin="00:05:29,946">Denne har &#229; gj&#248;re med...</p>
      <p end="00:05:33,533" begin="00:05:32,741">- Ditt prosjekt.</p>
      <p end="00:05:36,369" begin="00:05:33,533">- Ingen p&#229;virkning. Jeg trodde det var <span tts:fontStyle="italic">v&#229;rt</span> prosjekt.</p>
      <p end="00:05:37,120" begin="00:05:36,369">- Joda.</p>
      <p end="00:05:38,663" begin="00:05:37,120">Det er "No Impact Man".</p>
      <p end="00:05:41,708" begin="00:05:38,663">Det er hans bok og prosjekt og han er "No Impact Man".</p>
      <p end="00:05:46,379" begin="00:05:41,708">Men for &#229;... Men prosjektet handler om v&#229;r familie som gj&#248;r dette.</p>
      <p end="00:05:58,099" begin="00:05:46,379">[Togst&#248;y]</p>
      <p end="00:05:59,955" begin="00:05:58,099">- For to uker siden, p&#229; dag &#233;n av prosjektet-</p>
      <p end="00:06:03,618" begin="00:05:59,955">-stoppet vi med &#229; bruke karbonproduserende transport-</p>
      <p end="00:06:11,246" begin="00:06:05,231">-som betyr ingen bruk av fly, undergrunnsbane, taxi og heiser.</p>
      <p end="00:06:14,032" begin="00:06:12,200">Folk tenker p&#229; hvorfor vi g&#229;r til det ekstreme.</p>
      <p end="00:06:16,117" begin="00:06:14,032">Ikke alle kommer til &#229; g&#229; s&#229; langt.</p>
      <p end="00:06:19,485" begin="00:06:16,117">Alt dette handler om &#229; oppleve hele spekteret.</p>
      <p end="00:06:23,094" begin="00:06:19,485">For &#229; se hvilke ting vi virkelig er villige til &#229; gi opp.</p>
      <p end="00:06:26,419" begin="00:06:23,094">P&#229; slutten kommer vi ut og ser p&#229; hva vi er villige til &#229; beholde.</p>
      <p end="00:06:28,379" begin="00:06:26,419">Hva fjerner vi; hva var for vanskelig og ikke for vanskelig.</p>
      <p end="00:06:37,305" begin="00:06:33,510">Paradigmet er redusering, gjenbruk og resirkulering.</p>
      <p end="00:06:39,474" begin="00:06:37,305">Det f&#248;rste er redusering.</p>
      <p end="00:06:41,570" begin="00:06:39,474">Redusere v&#229;rt forbruk, ikke sant?</p>
      <p end="00:06:43,978" begin="00:06:41,893">Jeg tenker at:</p>
      <p end="00:06:48,608" begin="00:06:43,978">"Jeg kan ikke klare meg uten dette og denne".</p>
      <p end="00:06:52,796" begin="00:06:48,608">S&#229; det handler om &#229; klare seg uten alt.</p>
      <p end="00:06:53,384" begin="00:06:52,796">[Hunder bjeffer]</p>
      <p end="00:06:54,447" begin="00:06:53,384">- Kommer inn og ser p&#229; hvor stor TV-en er.</p>
      <p end="00:06:55,657" begin="00:06:54,447">- Ja, kom inn.</p>
      <p end="00:06:57,617" begin="00:06:55,657">- Hva skjedde?</p>
      <p end="00:06:59,151" begin="00:06:57,617">- De tar med seg TV-en.</p>
      <p end="00:07:00,621" begin="00:06:59,151">- Den g&#229;r ut.</p>
      <p end="00:07:01,703" begin="00:07:00,621">[Barnet klynker]</p>
      <p end="00:07:02,829" begin="00:07:01,703">- Vi skal bare ikke ha TV.</p>
      <p end="00:07:05,404" begin="00:07:02,829">Vi skal v&#230;re uten den.</p>
      <p end="00:07:06,152" begin="00:07:05,404">- Ja.</p>
      <p end="00:07:08,791" begin="00:07:06,152">- Mor er litt avhengig av TV.</p>
      <p end="00:07:10,289" begin="00:07:08,791">[Hund bjeffer]</p>
      <p end="00:07:15,218" begin="00:07:12,902">- Jeg blir 40 &#229;r denne sommeren og det var s&#229; mange ting-</p>
      <p end="00:07:18,346" begin="00:07:15,218">-ang&#229;ende m&#229;ten jeg levde livet mitt p&#229;-</p>
      <p end="00:07:21,766" begin="00:07:18,346">-spesielt med Isabella, som jeg &#248;nsket &#229; endre p&#229;.</p>
      <p end="00:07:23,560" begin="00:07:21,766">Jeg tok en grundig test av blodet mitt-</p>
      <p end="00:07:27,063" begin="00:07:23,560">-og den viste at hvis jeg ikke endret spisevanene mine-</p>
      <p end="00:07:32,963" begin="00:07:27,063">-kunne jeg utvikle diabetes, og jeg hadde lavt thyroid-niv&#229;.</p>
      <p end="00:07:36,739" begin="00:07:32,963">Og det skjedde samtidig med min 40-&#229;rsdag.</p>
      <p end="00:07:41,035" begin="00:07:36,739">Det er et punkt i livet hvor man tenker at:</p>
      <p end="00:07:45,371" begin="00:07:41,035">"Hva &#248;nsker jeg min andre halvdel av livet mitt &#229; se ut som?"</p>
      <p end="00:07:47,374" begin="00:07:45,371">Siden den f&#248;rste halvdelen er gjennomf&#248;rt.</p>
      <p end="00:07:48,960" begin="00:07:47,374">Tikk-takk.</p>
      <p end="00:07:52,297" begin="00:07:49,837">- [Colin] Prosjektet foreg&#229;r i faser.</p>
      <p end="00:07:55,425" begin="00:07:52,297">Jeg er ikke en oppl&#230;rt milj&#248;forkjemper s&#229; jeg l&#230;rer p&#229; veien.</p>
      <p end="00:07:58,678" begin="00:07:55,425">Akkurat n&#229; jobber vi med s&#248;ppelet v&#229;rt.</p>
      <p end="00:08:03,433" begin="00:07:58,678">Den gjennomsnittlige amerikaner lager 725 kg med s&#248;ppel &#229;rlig.</p>
      <p end="00:08:06,227" begin="00:08:03,433">Vi pr&#248;ver &#229; redusere det til null.</p>
      <p end="00:08:15,361" begin="00:08:06,227">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="00:08:18,282" begin="00:08:15,361">Det er sertifisert organisk biodynamikk p&#229; Hawthorne Valley Farm.</p>
      <p end="00:08:19,077" begin="00:08:18,282">- Ja.</p>
      <p end="00:08:20,575" begin="00:08:19,077">- Jeg skal sjekke om vi kan, som familie-</p>
      <p end="00:08:24,454" begin="00:08:20,575">-dra dit og bo der noen dager og melde oss som frivillige.</p>
      <p end="00:08:25,955" begin="00:08:24,454">Er det greit?</p>
      <p end="00:08:27,958" begin="00:08:25,955">- Ja, kj&#230;re. Det h&#248;res ut som en god id&#233;.</p>
      <p end="00:08:30,043" begin="00:08:27,958">[Begge ler]</p>
      <p end="00:08:33,922" begin="00:08:30,043">- St&#248;rstedelen av v&#229;rt s&#248;ppel er matemballasje og matrester.</p>
      <p end="00:08:35,924" begin="00:08:33,922">Det som er bra med et marked-</p>
      <p end="00:08:38,259" begin="00:08:35,924">-er at mesteparten selges uten emballasje.</p>
      <p end="00:08:41,054" begin="00:08:38,259">Det er enkelt &#229; kj&#248;pe ting der uten &#229; lage s&#248;ppel.</p>
      <p end="00:08:42,805" begin="00:08:41,054">- Ingen p&#229;virkning p&#229; milj&#248;et?</p>
      <p end="00:08:44,557" begin="00:08:42,805">- Nei.</p>
      <p end="00:08:45,266" begin="00:08:44,557">- Virkelig?</p>
      <p end="00:08:46,184" begin="00:08:45,266">- Ja.</p>
      <p end="00:08:47,560" begin="00:08:46,184">- Da kan du ikke f&#229; denne posen.</p>
      <p end="00:08:48,895" begin="00:08:47,560">- Takk!</p>
      <p end="00:08:51,272" begin="00:08:48,895">Hvordan skal jeg si dette uten &#229; h&#248;res ut som en drittsekk?</p>
      <p end="00:08:54,501" begin="00:08:51,272">Jeg blir d&#229;rlig av &#229; se ting bli individuelt pakket inn i plastikk.</p>
      <p end="00:08:56,515" begin="00:08:54,501">Hvor er de som selger mark?</p>
      <p end="00:08:58,473" begin="00:08:56,527">- Hva skal du ha mark for?<br/>Jeg vet ikke om jeg...</p>
      <p end="00:09:00,531" begin="00:08:58,488">- Kan jeg fortelle deg det senere?</p>
      <p end="00:09:03,026" begin="00:09:00,531">Markene lager kompost raskere.</p>
      <p end="00:09:06,454" begin="00:09:03,779">- Kj&#230;re, jeg synes ikke noe om dette.</p>
      <p end="00:09:09,131" begin="00:09:06,454">- Ok. Vi kan snakke om det.</p>
      <p end="00:09:11,209" begin="00:09:09,761">Michelle!</p>
      <p end="00:09:11,793" begin="00:09:11,209">- Ja?</p>
      <p end="00:09:13,211" begin="00:09:11,793">- Vil du se markene?</p>
      <p end="00:09:16,446" begin="00:09:14,879">[Isabella fniser]</p>
      <p end="00:09:21,344" begin="00:09:19,046">Ser du markene snor seg rundt?</p>
      <p end="00:09:23,371" begin="00:09:21,344">- Ja. Og hvordan kan du v&#230;re sikker p&#229; at de ikke kommer seg ut?</p>
      <p end="00:09:24,397" begin="00:09:23,371">- Det klarer de ikke.</p>
      <p end="00:09:25,014" begin="00:09:24,397">[Barnet mumler]</p>
      <p end="00:09:26,436" begin="00:09:25,014">- Vent. Er det ikke et lokk?</p>
      <p end="00:09:28,885" begin="00:09:26,436">- Jo, det stemmer.</p>
      <p end="00:09:29,592" begin="00:09:28,885">- Vi legger p&#229; lokket.</p>
      <p end="00:09:31,046" begin="00:09:29,592">- Isabella ser p&#229; dem.</p>
      <p end="00:09:33,315" begin="00:09:31,046">- Ok. Naturen...</p>
      <p end="00:09:34,951" begin="00:09:33,315">[Colin ler]</p>
      <p end="00:09:39,463" begin="00:09:34,951">Mamma liker egentlig ikke naturen, men det gj&#248;r pappa.</p>
      <p end="00:09:41,032" begin="00:09:39,463">[Colin ler]</p>
      <p end="00:09:44,701" begin="00:09:42,324">- Bleie.</p>
      <p end="00:09:51,374" begin="00:09:44,701">Bleie laget av ull; organisk ull og lam som er behandlet fint.</p>
      <p end="00:09:53,788" begin="00:09:51,374">Jeg sjekket alt dette.</p>
      <p end="00:09:57,088" begin="00:09:55,712">Det finnes fem forskjellige teknikker-</p>
      <p end="00:10:03,261" begin="00:09:57,088">-og man har bikinibretten, og englebretten, og s&#229; videre.</p>
      <p end="00:10:05,972" begin="00:10:03,261">Vi pr&#248;ver englebretten.</p>
      <p end="00:10:09,642" begin="00:10:05,972">Det er mye forvirring om hva av t&#248;ybleier eller engangsbleier-</p>
      <p end="00:10:11,477" begin="00:10:09,642">-er bedre for milj&#248;et.</p>
      <p end="00:10:16,190" begin="00:10:11,477">Og industribetalte studier viser at det ikke spiller noe rolle.</p>
      <p end="00:10:17,317" begin="00:10:16,190">Men faktum er at-</p>
      <p end="00:10:21,821" begin="00:10:17,317">-vi dumper 49 millioner plastikkbleier p&#229; s&#248;ppeldyngen hver dag.</p>
      <p end="00:10:24,949" begin="00:10:21,821">Det er den tredje st&#248;rste kilden til s&#248;ppel p&#229; s&#248;ppeldyngen.</p>
      <p end="00:10:26,034" begin="00:10:24,949">[Isabella snakker]</p>
      <p end="00:10:27,494" begin="00:10:26,034">- F&#248;les det ikke annerledes, baby?</p>
      <p end="00:10:29,037" begin="00:10:27,494">- Det er altfor morsomt!</p>
      <p end="00:10:30,955" begin="00:10:29,037">- Altfor morsomt...</p>
      <p end="00:10:33,374" begin="00:10:30,955">La oss se.</p>
      <p end="00:10:34,459" begin="00:10:33,374">Se her!</p>
      <p end="00:10:35,377" begin="00:10:34,459">- Oi!</p>
      <p end="00:10:37,837" begin="00:10:35,377">- Se der, da!</p>
      <p end="00:10:40,423" begin="00:10:37,837">Se p&#229; deg, da!</p>
      <p end="00:10:41,924" begin="00:10:40,423">- Det gr&#248;nne &#229;rhundrets baby.</p>
      <p end="00:10:43,051" begin="00:10:41,924">- Ha ha.</p>
      <p end="00:10:44,344" begin="00:10:43,051">[Michelle ler]</p>
      <p end="00:10:45,803" begin="00:10:44,344">[Klapping]</p>
      <p end="00:10:50,224" begin="00:10:46,496">- Vi drar hit hver s&#248;ndag og spiser frokost og vi elsker det.</p>
      <p end="00:10:55,813" begin="00:10:50,224">Men som en del av v&#229;rt prosjekt-</p>
      <p end="00:11:00,860" begin="00:10:55,813">-faser vi ut alt inkludert restaurantbes&#248;k.</p>
      <p end="00:11:03,905" begin="00:11:00,860">So dette er v&#229;rt siste m&#229;ltid hos <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Pasti's</span>-</p>
      <p end="00:11:07,700" begin="00:11:03,905">-og v&#229;rt siste m&#229;ltid i en restaurant sammen.</p>
      <p end="00:11:10,745" begin="00:11:07,700">- Vi skal spise mat fra innenfor en radius p&#229; kun 250 miles-</p>
      <p end="00:11:14,999" begin="00:11:10,745">-s&#229; <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Pasti's</span> i seg selv er ikke et problem, men for eksempel-</p>
      <p end="00:11:20,880" begin="00:11:14,999">-hveten og br&#248;det kommer sannsynligvis fra de store slettene som er langt unna.</p>
      <p end="00:11:25,968" begin="00:11:20,880">S&#229; det er problemet.</p>
      <p end="00:11:28,679" begin="00:11:25,968">Maten kommer fra overalt-</p>
      <p end="00:11:31,516" begin="00:11:28,679">-og vi pr&#248;ver &#229; spise lokalmat.</p>
      <p end="00:11:34,436" begin="00:11:31,516">Vi kan spise alt vi har unntatt krydderet-</p>
      <p end="00:11:37,605" begin="00:11:34,436">-fordi det varer hele &#229;ret.</p>
      <p end="00:11:38,856" begin="00:11:37,605">L&#248;k er ikke et problem.</p>
      <p end="00:11:39,982" begin="00:11:38,856">Hvitl&#248;k er ikke et problem.</p>
      <p end="00:11:42,818" begin="00:11:39,982">Squash er ikke et problem.</p>
      <p end="00:11:44,821" begin="00:11:42,818">Poteter er ikke et problem.</p>
      <p end="00:11:48,574" begin="00:11:44,821">Vi hadde baconpoteter forrige uke i tre dager.</p>
      <p end="00:11:51,869" begin="00:11:48,574">- Jeg har stoppet &#229; spise kj&#248;tt, men jeg spiser fortsatt fisk.</p>
      <p end="00:11:56,332" begin="00:11:51,869">Forrige kveld startet med ingenting av kj&#248;tt, fisk eller noe.</p>
      <p end="00:11:59,169" begin="00:11:56,332">Av trappene-</p>
      <p end="00:12:01,254" begin="00:11:59,169">-scooteren og ikke noe s&#248;ppel-</p>
      <p end="00:12:03,673" begin="00:12:01,254">-s&#229; m&#229; jeg si at maten er det vanskeligste.</p>
      <p end="00:12:07,760" begin="00:12:03,673">Det er vanskelig akkurat n&#229;, jeg vil bare g&#229; og spise noe godt.</p>
      <p end="00:12:09,762" begin="00:12:07,760">- Hvorfor er maten det vanskeligste &#229; h&#229;ndtere?</p>
      <p end="00:12:14,642" begin="00:12:11,931">- Fordi jeg f&#229;r ikke spise noe som smaker godt.</p>
      <p end="00:12:17,353" begin="00:12:14,642">[Begge ler]</p>
      <p end="00:12:22,650" begin="00:12:19,313">- Vi sitter fast med k&#229;l og rotgr&#248;nnsaker-</p>
      <p end="00:12:25,945" begin="00:12:22,650">-helt til vinteren er ferdig og v&#229;ren kommer.</p>
      <p end="00:12:27,321" begin="00:12:25,945">Hei, Ryan!</p>
      <p end="00:12:29,657" begin="00:12:27,321">Jeg kommer snart tilbake for &#229; kj&#248;pe melk.</p>
      <p end="00:12:31,784" begin="00:12:29,657">Jeg har altfor mye &#229; b&#230;re allerede.</p>
      <p end="00:12:34,579" begin="00:12:31,784">- Vi ser deg senere!</p>
      <p end="00:12:38,291" begin="00:12:34,579">Fyren som de gir mine eggkartonger til er ikke her.</p>
      <p end="00:12:40,918" begin="00:12:38,291">Transport av mat skaper mye karbonutslipp.</p>
      <p end="00:12:43,859" begin="00:12:40,918">Her i USA har den gjennomsnittlige maten-</p>
      <p end="00:12:47,720" begin="00:12:43,859">-reist 1500 miles fra g&#229;rden til flyet.</p>
      <p end="00:12:49,677" begin="00:12:47,720">Disse har flotte epler.</p>
      <p end="00:12:51,804" begin="00:12:49,677">Jeg lurer p&#229; hva din favoritt er?</p>
      <p end="00:12:54,140" begin="00:12:51,804">- [Mannlig kunde] Winesap-eplene kommer til &#229;-</p>
      <p end="00:12:54,182" begin="00:12:54,140">-bl&#229;se taket av huset.</p>
      <p end="00:12:56,114" begin="00:12:54,182">Men det er ogs&#229; mange andre grunner til &#229; spise lokalmat.</p>
      <p end="00:12:59,818" begin="00:12:56,114">For eksempel for &#229; bevare g&#229;rdene v&#229;re.</p>
      <p end="00:13:03,524" begin="00:12:59,818">Grunnen til at vi er vegetarianere er fordi verdens kj&#248;ttspising er ansvarlig-</p>
      <p end="00:13:08,520" begin="00:13:03,524">-for mer klimagasser enn noe annet inkludert transport.</p>
      <p end="00:13:14,494" begin="00:13:11,365">- Det finnes ikke lokalplantet kaffe, s&#229; jeg m&#229; droppe det.</p>
      <p end="00:13:17,580" begin="00:13:14,494">S&#229; i dag pr&#248;ver jeg Iced Colada Espresso for siste gang.</p>
      <p end="00:13:20,750" begin="00:13:17,580">Jeg er redd for at jeg sprekker og ikke klarer &#229; gjennomf&#248;re det.</p>
      <p end="00:13:25,296" begin="00:13:20,750">Og s&#229; er jeg redd for Colins vrede.</p>
      <p end="00:13:27,314" begin="00:13:25,296">Det urorer han n&#229;r jeg sprekker-</p>
      <p end="00:13:31,260" begin="00:13:27,314">-fordi det f&#229;r han til &#229; f&#248;le at hele prosjektet g&#229;r i vasken.</p>
      <p end="00:13:34,597" begin="00:13:31,260">Dette er enkelt for Colin, men et herk for meg.</p>
      <p end="00:13:36,641" begin="00:13:34,597">Maten og koffeinet.</p>
      <p end="00:13:40,353" begin="00:13:36,641">Det er mammas tredje og siste Iced Colada Espresso.</p>
      <p end="00:13:41,894" begin="00:13:40,353">N&#229; tar vi av!</p>
      <p end="00:13:47,068" begin="00:13:44,774">F&#248;ler meg bra!</p>
      <p end="00:13:49,070" begin="00:13:47,068">Herregud! Mye bedre.</p>
      <p end="00:13:55,593" begin="00:13:49,070">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="00:14:07,088" begin="00:14:03,251">- [Colin] En del av det &#229; spise lokalt er &#229; bli kjent med de lokale b&#248;ndene-</p>
      <p end="00:14:09,048" begin="00:14:07,088">-som man f&#229;r maten sin i fra.</p>
      <p end="00:14:12,494" begin="00:14:09,048">Vi drar for &#229; m&#248;te Ronnie p&#229; <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Ronnie Brook Farm-</span></p>
      <p end="00:14:15,989" begin="00:14:12,494">-og alle hans kyr.</p>
      <p end="00:14:18,933" begin="00:14:15,989">Dette er f&#248;rste gang jeg har v&#230;rt-</p>
      <p end="00:14:28,484" begin="00:14:18,933">-p&#229; et ikke-selvstyrt transportmiddel p&#229; over en m&#229;ned.</p>
      <p end="00:14:29,986" begin="00:14:28,484">S&#229; det er litt morsomt.</p>
      <p end="00:14:30,945" begin="00:14:29,986">Tut-tut!</p>
      <p end="00:14:32,196" begin="00:14:30,945">[Latter]</p>
      <p end="00:14:39,662" begin="00:14:32,196">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="00:14:40,997" begin="00:14:39,662">- [Bonde] Hver ku har et navn.</p>
      <p end="00:14:42,414" begin="00:14:40,997">Dette er Thelma.</p>
      <p end="00:14:45,418" begin="00:14:42,414">- [Colin] Hei, jenta mi.</p>
      <p end="00:14:49,797" begin="00:14:46,079">Er forholdet til dyrene en grunn til at du driver med dette?</p>
      <p end="00:14:52,050" begin="00:14:49,797">- Det er grunnen til at vi startet med dette.</p>
      <p end="00:14:55,678" begin="00:14:52,050">Kona mi sier at da min s&#248;nn ble f&#248;dt, m&#229;tte jeg melke kyrne.</p>
      <p end="00:14:57,930" begin="00:14:55,678">Jeg kunne ikke ta henne med til sykehuset.</p>
      <p end="00:14:58,718" begin="00:14:57,930">[Colin ler]</p>
      <p end="00:15:00,349" begin="00:14:58,718">Jeg visste ikke... Jeg husket ikke den.</p>
      <p end="00:15:03,394" begin="00:15:00,349">[Colin ler]</p>
      <p end="00:15:05,396" begin="00:15:03,394">- La oss snakke om organisk.</p>
      <p end="00:15:07,397" begin="00:15:05,396">Du har ikke organisk merket p&#229; produktene dine.</p>
      <p end="00:15:12,111" begin="00:15:07,397">Hvorfor ikke det og hva mener du om det som er organisk?</p>
      <p end="00:15:15,364" begin="00:15:12,111">- Jeg mener organisk er bra.</p>
      <p end="00:15:18,409" begin="00:15:15,364">Det ene som jeg er i mot n&#229;r det gjelder organisk-</p>
      <p end="00:15:20,870" begin="00:15:18,409">-er at man ikke kan behandle kyrne ved sykdomsutbrudd. - Akkurat.</p>
      <p end="00:15:22,079" begin="00:15:20,870">[Kremter]</p>
      <p end="00:15:25,166" begin="00:15:22,079">- Det er det eneste jeg ikke kan v&#230;re med p&#229;.</p>
      <p end="00:15:27,627" begin="00:15:25,166">- Som er hva? Forklar det til meg.</p>
      <p end="00:15:31,797" begin="00:15:27,627">- Hvis en ku blir syk, kan man ikke bruke antibiotika.</p>
      <p end="00:15:35,051" begin="00:15:31,797">Jeg kan ikke la kyrne d&#248;.</p>
      <p end="00:15:38,721" begin="00:15:35,051">Diss kyrne har v&#230;rt de samme for mange generasjoner.</p>
      <p end="00:15:42,016" begin="00:15:38,721">- J&#248;ss!</p>
      <p end="00:15:45,019" begin="00:15:42,016">Hei, kj&#230;re!</p>
      <p end="00:15:46,437" begin="00:15:45,019">S&#229; la meg sp&#248;rre deg om dette.</p>
      <p end="00:15:49,106" begin="00:15:46,437">S&#229; alt du sier... La oss g&#229; til den andre enden.</p>
      <p end="00:15:53,110" begin="00:15:49,106">Folk er ivrige p&#229; organisk mat.</p>
      <p end="00:15:55,821" begin="00:15:53,110">- Det viktigste... Grunnen til at lokalmat er viktig-</p>
      <p end="00:15:58,741" begin="00:15:55,821">-er fordi at jeg vil gj&#248;re n&#230;ringskjeden leselig.</p>
      <p end="00:16:00,576" begin="00:15:58,741">Hvis jeg kj&#248;per en drue fra deg-</p>
      <p end="00:16:01,843" begin="00:16:00,576">-da vil jeg se hva du har gjort med den.</p>
      <p end="00:16:03,859" begin="00:16:01,843">Man er ikke n&#248;dvendigvis sertifisert organisk-</p>
      <p end="00:16:07,067" begin="00:16:03,859">-men alt man har er organisk eller bedre.</p>
      <p end="00:16:11,150" begin="00:16:07,067">N&#229;r det gjelder melk s&#229; b&#248;r det v&#230;re lokalt-</p>
      <p end="00:16:15,791" begin="00:16:12,401">-og man m&#229; dra og se behandlingen av dyrene.</p>
      <p end="00:16:17,343" begin="00:16:15,791">Man b&#248;r dra og se p&#229; det!</p>
      <p end="00:16:21,059" begin="00:16:17,343">[Folk snakker]</p>
      <p end="00:16:26,341" begin="00:16:21,059">[Biler kj&#248;rer forbi]</p>
      <p end="00:16:30,648" begin="00:16:27,603">- [Colin] Dette er en fritata med bare lokalprodukter.</p>
      <p end="00:16:34,277" begin="00:16:30,648">Rotgr&#248;nnsakene kommer fra en g&#229;rd utenfor byen.</p>
      <p end="00:16:36,987" begin="00:16:34,277">R&#248;dk&#229;len kommer ogs&#229; fra utenfor New York City.</p>
      <p end="00:16:42,743" begin="00:16:36,987">Eggene og osten er ogs&#229; fra utenfor byen!</p>
      <p end="00:16:44,036" begin="00:16:42,743">- [Michelle] H&#248;rte du telefonen ringe?</p>
      <p end="00:16:44,787" begin="00:16:44,036">- Jeg gjorde det.</p>
      <p end="00:16:45,788" begin="00:16:44,787">- Det var Robin.</p>
      <p end="00:16:46,330" begin="00:16:45,788">- Jaha?</p>
      <p end="00:16:49,326" begin="00:16:46,330">Det de &#248;nsker &#229; gj&#248;re er-</p>
      <p end="00:16:51,539" begin="00:16:49,326">-&#229; f&#229; dette til &#229; v&#230;re forsidestoff.</p>
      <p end="00:16:52,670" begin="00:16:51,539">- Ja?</p>
      <p end="00:16:54,797" begin="00:16:52,670">Men tidlig mandag morgen, s&#229;nn cirka klokken syv-</p>
      <p end="00:16:57,466" begin="00:16:54,797">-trenger Robin kladden ferdig.</p>
      <p end="00:17:04,640" begin="00:16:57,466">Jeg f&#248;ler meg s&#229; svekket av kaffestoppen-</p>
      <p end="00:17:06,767" begin="00:17:04,640">-at jeg f&#248;ler at det kommer til &#229; g&#229; utover jobben min.</p>
      <p end="00:17:07,435" begin="00:17:06,767">- Jaha?</p>
      <p end="00:17:09,644" begin="00:17:07,435">- Jeg mener dette er en veldig viktig story.</p>
      <p end="00:17:12,475" begin="00:17:09,644">- S&#229; hvorfor venter du ikke til du forteller meg...</p>
      <p end="00:17:14,358" begin="00:17:12,475">N&#229;r skal du starte?</p>
      <p end="00:17:15,526" begin="00:17:14,358">- Etter middagsfesten.</p>
      <p end="00:17:18,320" begin="00:17:15,526">- Hvorfor venter du ikke til da og s&#229; kan du avgj&#248;re?</p>
      <p end="00:17:20,003" begin="00:17:18,320">[Hund bjeffer]</p>
      <p end="00:17:23,325" begin="00:17:20,995">- Du tuller n&#229;?</p>
      <p end="00:17:27,037" begin="00:17:23,325">Det f&#248;les som at hodet mitt er i ferd med &#229; hoppe av resten av kroppen.</p>
      <p end="00:17:27,830" begin="00:17:27,037">[Skje faller i gulvet]</p>
      <p end="00:17:30,958" begin="00:17:27,830">Det kommer til &#229; hjelpe meg igjennom prosessen. Det kommer til &#229; bli mye stress-</p>
      <p end="00:17:33,252" begin="00:17:30,958">-og s&#229; hvorfor benytter jeg meg ikke av den hjelpen?</p>
      <p end="00:17:34,962" begin="00:17:33,252">- Et lite &#248;yeblikk.</p>
      <p end="00:17:40,176" begin="00:17:37,173">Det du egentlig mener er at du trenger kaffe akkurat n&#229;.</p>
      <p end="00:17:40,989" begin="00:17:40,176">Det har ikke noe med...<br/>- Jeg g&#229;r ut med hunden.</p>
      <p end="00:17:42,887" begin="00:17:41,802">&#197; ta meg en slurk.</p>
      <p end="00:17:45,139" begin="00:17:42,887">- S&#229; det er egentlig det du...</p>
      <p end="00:17:47,808" begin="00:17:45,139">- Ja, jeg vil g&#229; og bruke... Jeg vil ta meg en tur.</p>
      <p end="00:17:50,352" begin="00:17:48,851">- Jeg bryr meg ikke.</p>
      <p end="00:17:53,439" begin="00:17:50,352">- Men du bryr deg jo.</p>
      <p end="00:17:54,774" begin="00:17:53,439">- Du vet...</p>
      <p end="00:17:57,610" begin="00:17:54,774">- Jeg spiser kun lokalmat. Jeg lager ikke s&#248;ppel.</p>
      <p end="00:17:58,944" begin="00:17:57,610">Jeg spiser ikke noe...<br/><span tts:fontStyle="italic">- Vent...</span></p>
      <p end="00:17:59,898" begin="00:17:59,063">- Fremskritt!</p>
      <p end="00:18:03,616" begin="00:17:59,898">- Du spiser bare lokalmat, men hvem skaffer det, st&#229;r opp om morgenen-</p>
      <p end="00:18:04,867" begin="00:18:03,616">-og lager frokost til deg hver dag.</p>
      <p end="00:18:05,534" begin="00:18:04,867">- Du!</p>
      <p end="00:18:06,243" begin="00:18:05,534">- Lager lunsjen din.</p>
      <p end="00:18:06,695" begin="00:18:06,243">- Du!</p>
      <p end="00:18:07,391" begin="00:18:06,695">- Lager middagen din.</p>
      <p end="00:18:08,826" begin="00:18:07,391">- Det var ikke det jeg mente!</p>
      <p end="00:18:11,248" begin="00:18:08,826">- Og s&#229; vasker koppene n&#229;r vi er ferdige?</p>
      <p end="00:18:13,125" begin="00:18:11,248">- Jeg tar meg av det!</p>
      <p end="00:18:15,211" begin="00:18:13,125">- Det som egentlig skjedde var at Robin ringte deg-</p>
      <p end="00:18:17,713" begin="00:18:15,211">-og s&#229; tenkte du at dette er en unnskyldning.</p>
      <p end="00:18:19,757" begin="00:18:17,713">[Isabella klynker]</p>
      <p end="00:18:22,009" begin="00:18:19,757">- S&#229; du m&#229; nok... Du er sint p&#229; meg-</p>
      <p end="00:18:24,512" begin="00:18:22,009">-og jeg forteller deg at jeg skal g&#229; ut og ta vare p&#229; meg selv.</p>
      <p end="00:18:25,299" begin="00:18:24,512">- Du legger ordene i munnen min.</p>
      <p end="00:18:25,880" begin="00:18:25,299">- Ok, da. Greit!</p>
      <p end="00:18:26,931" begin="00:18:25,880">- Jeg sa ikke at jeg var det.</p>
      <p end="00:18:29,642" begin="00:18:26,931">- Jeg skal n&#229; ta vare p&#229; meg selv-</p>
      <p end="00:18:33,729" begin="00:18:29,642">-og g&#229; ut og ta en Iced Quad Espresso, og kanskje to, jeg vet ikke.</p>
      <p end="00:18:37,780" begin="00:18:33,729">- Jeg &#248;nsker ikke &#229; skuffe meg selv og alle andre.</p>
      <p end="00:18:39,280" begin="00:18:37,780">[Humrer]</p>
      <p end="00:18:46,116" begin="00:18:42,464">- Jeg brukte denne krydrede olivenoljen og det er rester av v&#229;r olivenolje-</p>
      <p end="00:18:48,327" begin="00:18:46,116">-for ganske snart kan vi ikke bruke olivenolje.</p>
      <p end="00:18:50,287" begin="00:18:48,327">- [Mannlig bes&#248;kende] Skal du leve uten str&#248;m?</p>
      <p end="00:18:50,829" begin="00:18:50,287">- Etter hvert.</p>
      <p end="00:18:51,372" begin="00:18:50,829">- Ja.</p>
      <p end="00:18:54,125" begin="00:18:51,372">- Hva med str&#248;m i andres leilighet?</p>
      <p end="00:18:56,418" begin="00:18:54,125">- [Colin] Hvis noen inviterer oss med p&#229; TV-titting hos seg-</p>
      <p end="00:18:58,963" begin="00:18:56,418">-s&#229; blir vi med p&#229; grunn av det sosiale.</p>
      <p end="00:19:00,047" begin="00:18:58,963">Jeg tigger ikke, men det er i n&#230;rheten.</p>
      <p end="00:19:00,359" begin="00:19:00,047">[Latter]</p>
      <p end="00:19:03,900" begin="00:19:03,391">- [Kvinnelig bes&#248;kende] Brukte kl&#230;r?</p>
      <p end="00:19:05,970" begin="00:19:03,900">- Brukte kl&#230;r er lovlig.</p>
      <p end="00:19:07,097" begin="00:19:05,970">- Ok.</p>
      <p end="00:19:11,141" begin="00:19:07,097">- Ingen nye materialer, men Michelle tror jeg &#248;nsker &#229; br&#229;stoppe.</p>
      <p end="00:19:13,602" begin="00:19:11,141">- Jeg skal ikke kj&#248;pe noe nytt p&#229; et helt &#229;r.</p>
      <p end="00:19:15,563" begin="00:19:13,957">Det har v&#230;rt fint &#229; slippe taket-</p>
      <p end="00:19:17,439" begin="00:19:15,563">-fordi jeg har v&#230;rt i stand til &#229; tenke gjennom alt.</p>
      <p end="00:19:18,440" begin="00:19:17,439">Hva bruker jeg-</p>
      <p end="00:19:19,859" begin="00:19:18,440">-og hva bruker jeg ikke?</p>
      <p end="00:19:23,445" begin="00:19:19,859">- [Kvinnelig bes&#248;kende] Det er en felles stil.</p>
      <p end="00:19:25,614" begin="00:19:23,445">[Latter]</p>
      <p end="00:19:26,824" begin="00:19:25,614">Vi er de overfladiske vennene.</p>
      <p end="00:19:28,993" begin="00:19:26,824">[Latter]</p>
      <p end="00:19:34,081" begin="00:19:28,993">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="00:19:34,999" begin="00:19:34,081">- [Kvinnelig bes&#248;kende] Godt jobbet!</p>
      <p end="00:19:39,746" begin="00:19:34,999">- [Colin] I starten savnet vi TV-en fordi det var en vane &#229; se p&#229; TV.</p>
      <p end="00:19:42,264" begin="00:19:39,746">Og det rommet er fylt med &#229; leve i &#248;yeblikket-</p>
      <p end="00:19:43,691" begin="00:19:42,264">-med venner og hverandre.</p>
      <p end="00:19:54,480" begin="00:19:43,691">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="00:20:03,444" begin="00:20:00,065">- Jeg lager maisgr&#248;t som vi har mye av.</p>
      <p end="00:20:05,321" begin="00:20:03,444">Du ser at jeg ikke lager s&#229; mye fordi-</p>
      <p end="00:20:08,240" begin="00:20:05,321">-det er ikke s&#229; mye vi kan f&#229; tak i lokalt.</p>
      <p end="00:20:14,163" begin="00:20:08,240">S&#229;, maisgr&#248;t blir det.</p>
      <p end="00:20:16,081" begin="00:20:14,163">- [Isabella] Mitt eple!</p>
      <p end="00:20:26,717" begin="00:20:25,424">Okey. Gi mamma et kyss.</p>
      <p end="00:20:28,302" begin="00:20:26,717">- Glad i deg!</p>
      <p end="00:20:29,803" begin="00:20:28,302">Jeg ser deg senere.</p>
      <p end="00:20:31,388" begin="00:20:29,803">Jeg skal p&#229; jobb.</p>
      <p end="00:20:46,153" begin="00:20:31,388">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="00:20:49,990" begin="00:20:46,153">- Jeg skrev i bloggen om hvordan man unng&#229;r &#229; lage s&#248;ppel.</p>
      <p end="00:20:53,202" begin="00:20:49,990">Ingen indisk mat og engangsbokser.</p>
      <p end="00:20:55,788" begin="00:20:53,202">Ingen kinesisk mat og engangsbokser.</p>
      <p end="00:20:58,374" begin="00:20:55,788">Ingen italiensk mat og engangsbokser.</p>
      <p end="00:21:01,502" begin="00:20:58,374">Ingen colabokser. Ingen plastikkvannflasker.</p>
      <p end="00:21:03,963" begin="00:21:01,502">Vi avslutter abonnementet p&#229; blader og aviser.</p>
      <p end="00:21:07,925" begin="00:21:03,963">Vi stopper alt av s&#248;ppelpost.</p>
      <p end="00:21:14,974" begin="00:21:07,925">Jeg ringer til alle selskapene og sp&#248;r om de ikke kan sende det til oss noe mer.</p>
      <p end="00:21:19,728" begin="00:21:14,974">Returnerer egg -og b&#230;rkartonger til markedet for resirkulering.</p>
      <p end="00:21:23,065" begin="00:21:19,728">Kj&#248;per melk i gjenbrukbare flasker.</p>
      <p end="00:21:26,735" begin="00:21:23,065">B&#230;rer p&#229; min ultrakule gjenbrukbare kopp og vannflaske-</p>
      <p end="00:21:30,447" begin="00:21:26,735">-som er en glasskrukke jeg fant p&#229; fyllingen.</p>
      <p end="00:21:36,037" begin="00:21:30,447">Bruker natron fra en resirkulerbar eske for &#229; pusse tennene.</p>
      <p end="00:21:38,872" begin="00:21:36,037">Bytter til t&#248;ybleier.</p>
      <p end="00:21:42,501" begin="00:21:38,872">Kj&#248;per mat fra hovedhyllene og fra det lokale markedet-</p>
      <p end="00:21:44,586" begin="00:21:42,501">-som er upakket og ferskt.</p>
      <p end="00:21:47,423" begin="00:21:44,586">Hvis jeg vil ha det som er inne i boksen, hvorfor trenger jeg boksen?</p>
      <p end="00:21:49,925" begin="00:21:47,423">Og inne i boksen er det en pose.</p>
      <p end="00:21:53,595" begin="00:21:49,925">Ingen engangs barberh&#248;vler og bladpatroner.</p>
      <p end="00:21:57,641" begin="00:21:53,595">Bruker gammelt t&#248;y isteden for papir.</p>
      <p end="00:22:01,228" begin="00:21:57,641">Har en markbinge for &#229; kompostere matrester.</p>
      <p end="00:22:06,817" begin="00:22:01,228">Det kan returneres til jorden istedenfor giftstoffer som siver fra s&#248;ppeldyngen.</p>
      <p end="00:22:08,902" begin="00:22:06,817">Her.</p>
      <p end="00:22:10,714" begin="00:22:08,902">- [Mann] Jeg tror du sa at de skal spise-</p>
      <p end="00:22:13,121" begin="00:22:10,714">-1,5 kg med matrester...</p>
      <p end="00:22:14,825" begin="00:22:13,121">- Hver uke, ja.</p>
      <p end="00:22:18,871" begin="00:22:14,825">For alt av produkter lagret vi alt s&#248;ppel for fire dager-</p>
      <p end="00:22:20,205" begin="00:22:18,871">-og det var cirka 360 liter.</p>
      <p end="00:22:23,375" begin="00:22:20,205">P&#229; fire dager s&#229; er det bare ekkelt.</p>
      <p end="00:22:26,378" begin="00:22:23,375">Dette er v&#229;r totale mengde med s&#248;ppel p&#229; en uke.</p>
      <p end="00:22:35,095" begin="00:22:30,501">[Isabella snakker i telefonen]</p>
      <p end="00:22:37,765" begin="00:22:35,095">Da har vi gjort unna s&#248;ppelfasen.<br/><span tts:fontStyle="italic">- Ja.</span></p>
      <p end="00:22:39,892" begin="00:22:37,765">- Og vi har gjort unna lokalmatfasen.</p>
      <p end="00:22:40,851" begin="00:22:39,892">- Ja.</p>
      <p end="00:22:44,063" begin="00:22:40,851">- Og n&#229; beveger vi oss inn i den b&#230;rekraftige forbruksfasen.</p>
      <p end="00:22:47,649" begin="00:22:44,063">- Hva med transport og alt det andre vi har gjort?</p>
      <p end="00:22:51,863" begin="00:22:47,649">- Ja, men alt det er ikke en del av fasene.</p>
      <p end="00:22:54,823" begin="00:22:51,863">[Latter]</p>
      <p end="00:22:56,492" begin="00:22:54,823">S&#229; n&#229; er vi inne i...</p>
      <p end="00:22:57,201" begin="00:22:56,492">- Okey.</p>
      <p end="00:22:58,520" begin="00:22:57,201">- Det handler om &#229; ikke-</p>
      <p end="00:23:01,997" begin="00:22:58,520">-p&#229;virke milj&#248;et gjennom kj&#248;p av ting.</p>
      <p end="00:23:06,168" begin="00:23:01,997">Den f&#248;rste regelen er at vi ikke kj&#248;per nye produkter, ikke sant?</p>
      <p end="00:23:09,963" begin="00:23:06,168">Men vi kan l&#229;ne, leie eller kj&#248;pe brukt.</p>
      <p end="00:23:11,548" begin="00:23:09,963">- M&#229; du p&#229; do?<br/>- Ja!</p>
      <p end="00:23:12,716" begin="00:23:11,548">- Skal du p&#229; do?</p>
      <p end="00:23:13,801" begin="00:23:12,716">- Nei!</p>
      <p end="00:23:16,595" begin="00:23:13,801">- Har du toalettpapir?</p>
      <p end="00:23:18,472" begin="00:23:16,595">Vi har ikke mer toalettpapir igjen.</p>
      <p end="00:23:20,057" begin="00:23:18,472">Har vi mer toalettpair?</p>
      <p end="00:23:22,184" begin="00:23:20,057">- [Colin] Nei.</p>
      <p end="00:23:25,271" begin="00:23:22,184">En ting som er vanskelig for en forbruker &#229; finne ut av-</p>
      <p end="00:23:27,691" begin="00:23:25,271">-er hva som er greit og ikke greit &#229; kj&#248;pe-</p>
      <p end="00:23:30,651" begin="00:23:27,691">-og hva som kan kastes og ikke kastes, ikke sant?</p>
      <p end="00:23:31,901" begin="00:23:30,651">- Ja.</p>
      <p end="00:23:36,054" begin="00:23:31,901">- Forskning er veldig vanskelig og ikke alle kan gj&#248;re alt.</p>
      <p end="00:23:36,885" begin="00:23:36,054">- Ja!</p>
      <p end="00:23:41,385" begin="00:23:36,885">- Men, men hvis man kutter ned p&#229; forbruket, s&#229; er tingene man ikke trenger...</p>
      <p end="00:23:42,103" begin="00:23:41,385">- Ja.</p>
      <p end="00:23:43,343" begin="00:23:42,103">- Du har allerede gjort det!</p>
      <p end="00:23:43,839" begin="00:23:43,343">- Ja!</p>
      <p end="00:23:45,625" begin="00:23:43,839">- Du trenger ikke &#229; forske.</p>
      <p end="00:23:46,339" begin="00:23:45,625">- Det trenger du ikke.</p>
      <p end="00:23:49,142" begin="00:23:46,339">- S&#229; hvis du oppdager at du ikke trenger toalettpapir-</p>
      <p end="00:23:51,321" begin="00:23:49,142">-kan du bare bruke t&#248;y om igjen.</p>
      <p end="00:23:51,934" begin="00:23:51,321">- Ja.</p>
      <p end="00:23:54,022" begin="00:23:51,934">- Ja. Du trenger ikke &#229; kj&#248;pe toalettpapir-</p>
      <p end="00:23:56,654" begin="00:23:54,081">-og du trenger ikke &#229; forske p&#229; det heller.</p>
      <p end="00:23:57,501" begin="00:23:56,654">- Nei!</p>
      <p end="00:23:58,475" begin="00:23:57,501">- Forst&#229;r du?</p>
      <p end="00:23:59,326" begin="00:23:58,475">- Ja!</p>
      <p end="00:24:00,532" begin="00:23:59,326">- Ja!</p>
      <p end="00:24:01,913" begin="00:24:00,532">- Vil du v&#230;re s&#229; grafisk, fordi...</p>
      <p end="00:24:04,125" begin="00:24:01,913">[Isabella ler]</p>
      <p end="00:24:06,431" begin="00:24:04,125">- Saken er at man vet ikke f&#248;r man har pr&#248;vd.</p>
      <p end="00:24:07,877" begin="00:24:06,431">- Jeg tror jeg mister jobben min.</p>
      <p end="00:24:09,672" begin="00:24:07,877">- Toalettpapir...</p>
      <p end="00:24:12,182" begin="00:24:09,672">[Michelle ler]</p>
      <p end="00:24:15,470" begin="00:24:12,182">- Og narr av v&#229;r offentlige helse, det kommer til &#229; bli...</p>
      <p end="00:24:17,141" begin="00:24:15,470">- [Colin] Eksperimentet varer i et &#229;r.</p>
      <p end="00:24:17,902" begin="00:24:17,141">- Akkurat.</p>
      <p end="00:24:20,464" begin="00:24:17,902">Kommer det ikke til &#229; gj&#248;re deg, <span tts:fontStyle="italic">No Impact Man</span>, s&#229; frynsete og tullete-</p>
      <p end="00:24:24,521" begin="00:24:20,464">-at du blir sett p&#229; som en frynsete tulling?</p>
      <p end="00:24:26,001" begin="00:24:24,521">Jeg bare sp&#248;r retorisk.</p>
      <p end="00:24:29,165" begin="00:24:26,001">- Men hvis jeg pr&#248;ver det og finner ut at det fungerer-</p>
      <p end="00:24:32,519" begin="00:24:29,165">-og det er bedre for milj&#248;et og det ikke er noe problem-</p>
      <p end="00:24:37,153" begin="00:24:32,519">-og at det kan utf&#248;res med samme hygiene som f&#248;r-</p>
      <p end="00:24:38,217" begin="00:24:37,153">-da forst&#229;r jeg ikke hvorfor det vil bli sett ned p&#229;.</p>
      <p end="00:24:39,282" begin="00:24:38,217">Men hvis jeg ikke pr&#248;ver det...</p>
      <p end="00:24:40,189" begin="00:24:39,282">- Okey.</p>
      <p end="00:24:41,411" begin="00:24:40,189">- Jeg vil ikke vite alt.</p>
      <p end="00:24:42,552" begin="00:24:41,411">- Ja.</p>
      <p end="00:24:43,538" begin="00:24:42,552">- Du forst&#229;r.</p>
      <p end="00:24:45,158" begin="00:24:43,538">[Isabella snakker]</p>
      <p end="00:24:46,714" begin="00:24:45,158">- Ja.</p>
      <p end="00:24:49,432" begin="00:24:46,714">Hva er negativt med toalettpapir?</p>
      <p end="00:24:53,264" begin="00:24:49,878">- Vi trenger tr&#230;rne v&#229;re for &#229; absorbere karbondioksid, men isteden-</p>
      <p end="00:24:56,981" begin="00:24:53,264">-kutter vi ned alle sammen for &#229; lage toalettpapir.</p>
      <p end="00:24:59,231" begin="00:24:56,981">En del av v&#229;rt eksperiment er &#229; sp&#248;rre om-</p>
      <p end="00:25:03,478" begin="00:24:59,231">-vi er n&#248;dt til &#229; v&#230;re en bruk og kast-kultur, ikke sant?</p>
      <p end="00:25:05,993" begin="00:25:03,478">Og toalett... Det er et ekstremtilfelle-</p>
      <p end="00:25:10,345" begin="00:25:05,993">-fordi vi ser p&#229; alle sider av denne "bruk og kast-heten"-</p>
      <p end="00:25:13,692" begin="00:25:10,345">-fordi denne bruk og kast-kulturen er et stort problem-</p>
      <p end="00:25:15,358" begin="00:25:13,692">-og hvis vi faktisk...</p>
      <p end="00:25:16,797" begin="00:25:15,358">Kanskje vi kan komme oss unna alt-</p>
      <p end="00:25:20,538" begin="00:25:16,797">-som vi kaster vekk.</p>
      <p end="00:25:24,113" begin="00:25:20,538">- Jeg tenkte i kveld at hvis du skal sp&#248;rre meg om &#229; gjennomf&#248;re dette-</p>
      <p end="00:25:27,396" begin="00:25:24,113">-s&#229; burde jeg f&#229;tt en premie eller en kupong-</p>
      <p end="00:25:29,289" begin="00:25:27,396">-som jeg kan bruke p&#229; noe.</p>
      <p end="00:25:33,646" begin="00:25:29,289">Men jeg vil egentlig ikke ha noe, s&#229; da var min neste tanke at-</p>
      <p end="00:25:37,613" begin="00:25:33,646">-jeg f&#248;lte tristheten p&#229; den ene siden av meg-</p>
      <p end="00:25:42,333" begin="00:25:37,613">-hvor den d&#248;de litt, og det f&#248;ltes som det bare var et hull der.</p>
      <p end="00:25:45,697" begin="00:25:42,333">- S&#229; hva er igjen?</p>
      <p end="00:25:51,450" begin="00:25:50,280">- Hva er det?</p>
      <p end="00:25:57,750" begin="00:25:51,450">- Det er alt vi skal gi bort etter at vi ryddet skapene.</p>
      <p end="00:26:00,263" begin="00:25:57,750">- Okey, er du klar?</p>
      <p end="00:26:08,942" begin="00:26:04,925">- Dette er redusering av inventar.</p>
      <p end="00:26:15,306" begin="00:26:12,403">[Michelle gisper]</p>
      <p end="00:26:18,628" begin="00:26:15,306">Jeg har aldri v&#230;rt her f&#248;r hvor de har satt opp en Marc Jacob-butikk.</p>
      <p end="00:26:21,959" begin="00:26:18,628">- Du har akkurat den samme vesken.<br/>- Nei, kj&#230;re.</p>
      <p end="00:26:24,802" begin="00:26:21,959">Jeg har den hvite "Sophia".</p>
      <p end="00:26:25,939" begin="00:26:24,802">- Og hva er det?</p>
      <p end="00:26:30,178" begin="00:26:25,939">- Den er ikke hvit. den er nesten brungr&#229;, men det er en helt forskjellig veske.</p>
      <p end="00:26:32,831" begin="00:26:30,178">[Bil tuter]</p>
      <p end="00:26:47,221" begin="00:26:44,897">Kanskje v&#229;r var litt st&#248;rre, men jeg vet ikke helt.</p>
      <p end="00:26:49,438" begin="00:26:47,221">Den minner meg om TV-en v&#229;r.</p>
      <p end="00:26:51,444" begin="00:26:49,438">[Humrer]</p>
      <p end="00:26:59,108" begin="00:26:55,925">- [Radiovert] Du er p&#229; New York offentlig radio WNYC FM og AM New York-</p>
      <p end="00:27:01,261" begin="00:26:59,108">-og WNYC.org.</p>
      <p end="00:27:04,742" begin="00:27:01,261">For det meste sol i Central Park klokken 10.</p>
      <p end="00:27:08,537" begin="00:27:04,742">Min f&#248;rste gjest i dag er <span tts:fontStyle="italic">No Impact Man</span>.</p>
      <p end="00:27:13,318" begin="00:27:08,537">Colin Beavan gikk opp 24 trappetrinn med deres vert-</p>
      <p end="00:27:18,686" begin="00:27:13,318">-som ikke er stolt av eller lei av &#229; unng&#229; og forbruke str&#248;m i en heis...</p>
      <p end="00:27:20,856" begin="00:27:18,686">For dere som har <span tts:fontStyle="italic">New York Times</span> liggende rundt-</p>
      <p end="00:27:23,553" begin="00:27:20,856">-kan dere ta ut seksjon F; hus og hjem-seksjonen.</p>
      <p end="00:27:27,210" begin="00:27:23,553">Der har du et stort, gr&#248;nt bilde av Colin Beavans leilighet-</p>
      <p end="00:27:28,822" begin="00:27:27,210">-med hans kone, barn og alt.</p>
      <p end="00:27:29,901" begin="00:27:28,822">[Musikk spilles]</p>
      <p end="00:27:31,961" begin="00:27:29,901">Et av de st&#248;rste bildene jeg har sett i <span tts:fontStyle="italic">New York Times</span>.</p>
      <p end="00:27:32,700" begin="00:27:31,961">[Latter]</p>
      <p end="00:27:35,573" begin="00:27:32,700">En av de minste leilighetene jeg har sett i <span tts:fontStyle="italic">New York Times</span>.</p>
      <p end="00:27:36,682" begin="00:27:36,127">[Latter]</p>
      <p end="00:27:38,510" begin="00:27:36,682">Jeg kj&#248;rte hjem fra Bryans show og jeg tenkte:</p>
      <p end="00:27:41,479" begin="00:27:38,510">"Jeg lurer p&#229; om noen av vennene mine s&#229; hva som sto i avisen-</p>
      <p end="00:27:47,433" begin="00:27:41,479">-og e-mailet meg for &#229; gratulere meg". Jeg fant 150 e-poster.</p>
      <p end="00:27:51,986" begin="00:27:47,433">Emnelinjen sier noe som "Hilsener fra <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Today's</span> show".</p>
      <p end="00:27:55,463" begin="00:27:51,986">
        <br/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Hei. Dette er Mary Noel. Jeg er producer for Bill Mark.</span>
      </p>
      <p end="00:27:59,485" begin="00:27:55,463">F&#248;rst var jeg spent, men etter &#229; ha sett p&#229; hvor mange det var-</p>
      <p end="00:28:05,381" begin="00:27:59,485">-og jeg ikke visste hva jeg skulle gj&#248;re, gikk jeg fra &#229; v&#230;re spent til livredd.</p>
      <p end="00:28:07,414" begin="00:28:05,381">Hei, Colin. Mitt navn er Julie-</p>
      <p end="00:28:09,448" begin="00:28:07,414">-og jeg jobber for Discovery Channel.</p>
      <p end="00:28:13,075" begin="00:28:09,448">Hei, Mr. Beavan, mitt navn er Abe Hagras, og jeg ringer fra Al Jazeera-</p>
      <p end="00:28:15,234" begin="00:28:13,075">-fra Washington D.C.</p>
      <p end="00:28:18,664" begin="00:28:15,234">Folk kontakter meg fra Australia, Colombia, Tyskland og Italia.</p>
      <p end="00:28:23,582" begin="00:28:18,664">- Han lager en story om familier som lever i New York-</p>
      <p end="00:28:26,579" begin="00:28:23,582">-og som er &#248;ko-effektive og milj&#248;messig gr&#248;nne familier.</p>
      <p end="00:28:29,747" begin="00:28:26,579">- [Kvinnelig intervjuer] Kan du snu deg litt mer mot meg?</p>
      <p end="00:28:31,900" begin="00:28:30,456">- Ser du?</p>
      <p end="00:28:37,086" begin="00:28:31,900">For &#229; ikke nevne italiensk og japansk TV.</p>
      <p end="00:28:39,741" begin="00:28:37,086">Intervju-foresp&#248;rsel fra en avis i Frankrike.</p>
      <p end="00:28:44,854" begin="00:28:39,741">- [Reporter snakker p&#229; fransk]</p>
      <p end="00:28:47,089" begin="00:28:44,854">- F&#248;r vi startet med dette, hadde jeg og Michelle...</p>
      <p end="00:28:49,539" begin="00:28:47,089">- [Radiovert] Du snakket om filosofien, hva er bak...</p>
      <p end="00:28:49,950" begin="00:28:49,539">- Okey.</p>
      <p end="00:28:50,582" begin="00:28:49,950">- "No Impact Man".</p>
      <p end="00:28:53,820" begin="00:28:50,582">Jeg tenker alltid p&#229; kollektive tiltak.</p>
      <p end="00:28:58,076" begin="00:28:53,820">Hva vi som et samfunn b&#248;r gj&#248;re, og lovene som b&#248;r endres.</p>
      <p end="00:29:00,695" begin="00:28:58,076">Men en av de tingene jeg har v&#230;rt svak p&#229;, som liberal-</p>
      <p end="00:29:01,632" begin="00:29:00,695">-er individuell handling.</p>
      <p end="00:29:03,816" begin="00:29:01,632">Hvorfor m&#229; jeg vente til Kongressen gj&#248;r noe?</p>
      <p end="00:29:06,311" begin="00:29:03,816">Hvorfor m&#229; jeg vente til de store selskapene gj&#248;r noe?</p>
      <p end="00:29:07,576" begin="00:29:06,311">Hvorfor gj&#248;r ikke jeg noe?</p>
      <p end="00:29:10,871" begin="00:29:07,576">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Times</span> f&#229;r det til &#229; h&#248;res ut som delvis endring av verden-</p>
      <p end="00:29:13,700" begin="00:29:10,871">-og delvis gimmick for din neste bok. Er det s&#229;nn?</p>
      <p end="00:29:15,625" begin="00:29:13,700">- Ja, helt klart.</p>
      <p end="00:29:17,926" begin="00:29:15,625">Jeg er den jeg er og dette er det jeg gj&#248;r.</p>
      <p end="00:29:23,070" begin="00:29:17,926">Men hvis jeg kan f&#248;re den energien jeg har som person-</p>
      <p end="00:29:25,644" begin="00:29:23,070">-i en retning som... Jeg sier dette med all ydmykhet.</p>
      <p end="00:29:29,156" begin="00:29:25,644">&#197; f&#248;re den energien i en retning som kan hjelpe verden-</p>
      <p end="00:29:31,731" begin="00:29:29,156">-er bedre enn &#229; f&#248;re den i en annen retning.</p>
      <p end="00:29:36,213" begin="00:29:31,731">Dette er hva en reporter fra <span tts:fontStyle="italic">New York Times</span> sier om prosjektet:</p>
      <p end="00:29:40,176" begin="00:29:36,213">"Det ser ut som en scene fra en gammeldags situasjonskomedie-</p>
      <p end="00:29:44,651" begin="00:29:40,176">-og en etisk sett grumsete &#248;velse i selvpromotering".</p>
      <p end="00:29:48,220" begin="00:29:44,651">Hun skrev alts&#229; at mulighetene er-</p>
      <p end="00:29:51,873" begin="00:29:48,220">-d&#229;rlig eller veldig d&#229;rlig.</p>
      <p end="00:29:53,116" begin="00:29:51,873">For leseren var dette veldig morsomt.</p>
      <p end="00:29:58,281" begin="00:29:53,116">Men jeg mener at dette underminerer folks mulighet til &#229; tenke p&#229; det.</p>
      <p end="00:30:00,404" begin="00:29:58,281">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="00:30:04,651" begin="00:30:00,404">Men hvis vi kalte det "&#229;ret jeg mistet 10 kilo uten &#229; g&#229; til treningsstudio"-</p>
      <p end="00:30:10,278" begin="00:30:04,651">-eller "&#229;ret vi ikke s&#229; p&#229; TV og ble mye bedre foreldre som f&#248;lger av det".</p>
      <p end="00:30:13,760" begin="00:30:10,278">Eller "&#229;ret vi spiste lokalt og sesongbasert-</p>
      <p end="00:30:17,457" begin="00:30:13,760">-og det endte med &#229; reversere min kones pre-diabetiske tilstand".</p>
      <p end="00:30:22,248" begin="00:30:17,457">Det er faktiske fordeler med &#229; leve milj&#248;bevisst.</p>
      <p end="00:30:27,789" begin="00:30:23,833">Dette er leserens meninger, ikke sant?</p>
      <p end="00:30:32,498" begin="00:30:27,789">379 kommentarer. Det er et stort antall kommentarer.</p>
      <p end="00:30:34,841" begin="00:30:32,498">"Ofre n&#229; eller senere. Jeg gj&#248;r allerede mye-</p>
      <p end="00:30:37,022" begin="00:30:34,841">-men planlegger &#229; gj&#248;re mye mer".</p>
      <p end="00:30:40,970" begin="00:30:37,022">Og denne sier: "Jeg kan ikke vente p&#229; &#229; f&#229; t&#248;rket r&#230;va med denne boken".</p>
      <p end="00:30:43,339" begin="00:30:40,970">Denne sier "D.D.J.R. Michelle"-</p>
      <p end="00:30:49,500" begin="00:30:43,339">-som jeg tror st&#229;r for "Dump Dette J&#230;vla Rassh&#248;let".</p>
      <p end="00:30:55,397" begin="00:30:49,500"><span tts:fontStyle="italic">Gawkers</span> til side som parodierer og sender ting opp som var i media.</p>
      <p end="00:30:58,043" begin="00:30:55,397">"Colin gr&#229;ter stille p&#229; toalettet".</p>
      <p end="00:31:00,752" begin="00:30:58,043">"Altfor fuktig til &#229; bevege seg; altfor stolt til &#229; t&#248;rke seg".</p>
      <p end="00:31:02,191" begin="00:31:00,752">[Latter]</p>
      <p end="00:31:04,782" begin="00:31:02,191">Det var morsomt, men kommentarene...</p>
      <p end="00:31:06,985" begin="00:31:04,782">Min f&#248;rste impuls var &#229; rive i stykker disse personene-</p>
      <p end="00:31:11,098" begin="00:31:06,985">-med brennende flammer imens jeg skriker: "Er dette nok p&#229;virkning for deg?"</p>
      <p end="00:31:13,352" begin="00:31:11,098">Jeg tvilte litt p&#229; meg selv for en liten stund.</p>
      <p end="00:31:16,366" begin="00:31:13,352">Jeg tenkte at det l&#248;nner seg, men kanskje det ikke gj&#248;r det.</p>
      <p end="00:31:18,323" begin="00:31:16,366">Kanskje det er filosofisk sett feil.</p>
      <p end="00:31:22,316" begin="00:31:18,323">Jeg har ogs&#229; f&#229;tt e-post fra milj&#248;forkjempere som sier at-</p>
      <p end="00:31:24,927" begin="00:31:22,316">-det er s&#229;nne som meg som f&#229;r resten til &#229; se ut som idioter.</p>
      <p end="00:31:31,508" begin="00:31:24,927">Er det mulig at jeg tar helt feil avgj&#248;relser?</p>
      <p end="00:31:36,996" begin="00:31:31,508">Ja, men man m&#229;... Jeg pr&#248;ver bare &#229;...</p>
      <p end="00:31:41,395" begin="00:31:36,996">Jeg vil sp&#248;rre meg selv... Det &#229; gj&#248;re hva samvittigheten...</p>
      <p end="00:31:44,747" begin="00:31:41,395">Jeg pr&#248;ver bare &#229; f&#248;lge det samvittigheten min sier.</p>
      <p end="00:31:49,526" begin="00:31:44,747">[Vann fra kranen]</p>
      <p end="00:31:53,038" begin="00:31:49,526">Jeg vet at jeg ikke kan gi meg n&#229; og svikte deg.</p>
      <p end="00:31:55,100" begin="00:31:53,038">Men det gj&#248;r at jeg ikke vil gj&#248;re det.</p>
      <p end="00:31:58,595" begin="00:31:55,100">- Jeg mener det er bra at vi har lest-</p>
      <p end="00:32:00,199" begin="00:31:58,595">-bloggen og slike ting.</p>
      <p end="00:32:03,748" begin="00:32:00,199">- En person fra jobben fortalte meg noe. Hun er en venn av meg.</p>
      <p end="00:32:07,016" begin="00:32:03,748">Men uansett hvor hun har v&#230;rt s&#229; snakker folk om dette.</p>
      <p end="00:32:10,436" begin="00:32:07,016">Om hvordan vi er falske og gale-</p>
      <p end="00:32:14,097" begin="00:32:10,436">-og hun bruker all sin tid p&#229; &#229; forsvare meg.</p>
      <p end="00:32:15,546" begin="00:32:14,097">Men det var en fyr som sa at-</p>
      <p end="00:32:21,068" begin="00:32:15,546">-hans kone aldri skulle ta meg i h&#229;nden igjen.</p>
      <p end="00:32:26,791" begin="00:32:21,068">Og hun snakket hele kvelden om hygienen og...</p>
      <p end="00:32:31,077" begin="00:32:26,791">Jeg forst&#229;r hvorfor de vil kritisere oss, men ikke hvorfor de vil hate oss.</p>
      <p end="00:32:32,224" begin="00:32:31,077">- Kj&#230;re, det er ikke... Jeg tror ikke de hater oss.</p>
      <p end="00:32:33,737" begin="00:32:32,224">- Se p&#229; det, du!</p>
      <p end="00:32:40,846" begin="00:32:37,373">- Helt tilfeldig ble jeg og Colin invitert p&#229; brunch-</p>
      <p end="00:32:45,833" begin="00:32:40,846">-av en kvinne, Kerry, fordi hun skriver om mat-</p>
      <p end="00:32:52,923" begin="00:32:45,833">-og det viser seg at p&#229; slutten s&#229; kommer hun frem og sier-</p>
      <p end="00:32:56,791" begin="00:32:52,923">-at hun har skrevet negativt om oss-</p>
      <p end="00:32:59,651" begin="00:32:56,791">-og hadde v&#230;rt en av de som hatet oss.</p>
      <p end="00:33:01,744" begin="00:32:59,651">Hun p&#229;st&#229;r at hun har endret synet sitt p&#229; oss.</p>
      <p end="00:33:02,801" begin="00:33:01,744">Jeg vet ikke.</p>
      <p end="00:33:04,356" begin="00:33:02,801">- [Kerry Trueman] Okey. La meg se om jeg kan f&#229; dette frem.</p>
      <p end="00:33:05,918" begin="00:33:04,356">"Jeg har fryktet dette &#248;yeblikket."</p>
      <p end="00:33:07,194" begin="00:33:05,918">"Jeg var redd for at du ville sp&#248;rre meg."</p>
      <p end="00:33:08,431" begin="00:33:07,194">[Michelle ler]</p>
      <p end="00:33:09,633" begin="00:33:08,431">- Du tuller n&#229;?</p>
      <p end="00:33:10,527" begin="00:33:09,633">- Herregud.</p>
      <p end="00:33:13,222" begin="00:33:10,527">"<span tts:fontStyle="italic">No Impact Man</span> har faktisk en p&#229;virkning"-</p>
      <p end="00:33:15,232" begin="00:33:13,222">-"men kanskje ikke den p&#229;virkningen han var ute etter".</p>
      <p end="00:33:17,360" begin="00:33:15,232">"Det var en gang da dyd var en premie i seg selv".</p>
      <p end="00:33:21,729" begin="00:33:17,360">"Akkurat n&#229; er den frivillige enkelheten bare en annen entrepreneurisk bedrift".</p>
      <p end="00:33:24,794" begin="00:33:21,729">"Det faktum at <span tts:fontStyle="italic">No Impact Mans</span> prangende omfavnelse av alt som er organisk"-</p>
      <p end="00:33:28,462" begin="00:33:24,809">-"skjedde ikke p&#229; en organisk m&#229;te, og det har jeg problemer med".</p>
      <p end="00:33:32,089" begin="00:33:28,462">"Imens <span tts:fontStyle="italic">No Impact Man</span> l&#248;per rundt og luftt&#248;rker rumpa for ettertiden"-</p>
      <p end="00:33:35,446" begin="00:33:32,089">-*s&#229; lever mindre fargerike folk liv med stille inspirasjon".</p>
      <p end="00:33:38,409" begin="00:33:36,707">[Puster ut h&#248;yt]</p>
      <p end="00:33:40,234" begin="00:33:38,409">Jeg stilte sp&#248;rsm&#229;l ved hans oppriktighet og motiver.</p>
      <p end="00:33:40,599" begin="00:33:40,234">- Ja.</p>
      <p end="00:33:46,438" begin="00:33:40,599">- Og det var en viss kvalitet i innlegget som fikk meg til &#229; g&#229; i feil retning.</p>
      <p end="00:33:54,212" begin="00:33:46,438">- Din kritikk i kritikkens sammenheng er veldig, veldig,veldig, veldig mild.</p>
      <p end="00:33:57,846" begin="00:33:54,212">Jeg forsto ikke helt hvorfor folk hatet oss eller hvorfor det var s&#229;...</p>
      <p end="00:33:58,683" begin="00:33:57,846">- Jeg har en teori.</p>
      <p end="00:33:59,601" begin="00:33:58,683">- Jeg forsto det ikke helt.</p>
      <p end="00:34:03,824" begin="00:33:59,601">- Basert p&#229; hva jeg selv har opplevd, s&#229; blir det sagt for mye-</p>
      <p end="00:34:07,749" begin="00:34:03,824">-men jeg tror det treffer en nerve hos mange.</p>
      <p end="00:34:10,384" begin="00:34:07,749">Bortsett fra det at folk f&#248;ler seg skyldige-</p>
      <p end="00:34:15,025" begin="00:34:10,384">-og defensive n&#229;r det gjelder deres forbrukervaner.</p>
      <p end="00:34:18,533" begin="00:34:15,025">Folk blir traumatisert hvis man foresl&#229;r-</p>
      <p end="00:34:21,484" begin="00:34:18,533">-at de b&#248;r klare seg uten visse ting.</p>
      <p end="00:34:24,365" begin="00:34:21,484">Hvis de tenker at...</p>
      <p end="00:34:25,875" begin="00:34:24,365">- Oppfatningen av at "Jeg trenger det!"</p>
      <p end="00:34:28,099" begin="00:34:25,875">- Det &#229; v&#230;re uten... Jeg trenger dette.<br/>- Men jeg trenger det.</p>
      <p end="00:34:31,313" begin="00:34:28,099">- Eller: "Jeg trenger det ikke; jeg vil ha det. Hvorfor skal jeg ikke f&#229; det?"</p>
      <p end="00:34:34,536" begin="00:34:31,313">Det er en god amerikaner.</p>
      <p end="00:34:57,848" begin="00:34:34,536">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="00:35:01,450" begin="00:34:57,848">
        <br/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Colin] En del av det med lokalmat er &#229; forbinde seg til hvordan det dyrkes.</span>
      </p>
      <p end="00:35:04,672" begin="00:35:01,450">S&#229; jeg snakket med den lokale samfunnshagen, og ventelisten-</p>
      <p end="00:35:07,435" begin="00:35:04,672">-for &#229; ha din egen tomt er veldig lang. Det kan ta flere &#229;r.</p>
      <p end="00:35:10,490" begin="00:35:07,435">Men det viser seg at det er bare en person i den hagen-</p>
      <p end="00:35:11,724" begin="00:35:10,490">-som dyrker gr&#248;nnsaker.</p>
      <p end="00:35:13,124" begin="00:35:11,724">Alle andre dyrker blomster.</p>
      <p end="00:35:17,521" begin="00:35:13,124">Og han var villig til &#229; ta meg med og l&#230;re meg opp.</p>
      <p end="00:35:19,117" begin="00:35:17,521">- [Meyer] Skal du hjelpe oss i hagen?</p>
      <p end="00:35:20,585" begin="00:35:19,117">- Ja!</p>
      <p end="00:35:22,047" begin="00:35:20,585">- Vi du dyrke ting?</p>
      <p end="00:35:23,958" begin="00:35:22,047">- Det er kompisen min, Meyer.</p>
      <p end="00:35:27,061" begin="00:35:23,958">V&#230;r forsiktig. Det er en rosebusk og den har torner.</p>
      <p end="00:35:28,649" begin="00:35:27,061">- [Meyer] Se, det stikker ut.<br/>- [Colin] Skarpe saker.</p>
      <p end="00:35:33,752" begin="00:35:30,573">- La oss snakke om hva vi h&#229;per p&#229; &#229; f&#229; gjort i dag.</p>
      <p end="00:35:34,813" begin="00:35:33,752">- Ja.</p>
      <p end="00:35:37,778" begin="00:35:34,813">Denne lille tomten skal v&#230;re persille.</p>
      <p end="00:35:42,056" begin="00:35:37,778">Kast det utover dette rektangelet-</p>
      <p end="00:35:46,644" begin="00:35:42,056">-og dekk det med den dybden som er riktig.</p>
      <p end="00:35:50,350" begin="00:35:46,644">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="00:35:52,647" begin="00:35:50,350">- N&#229; skal du f&#229; h&#248;re hva jeg gj&#248;r.</p>
      <p end="00:35:55,741" begin="00:35:52,647">Vi skal s&#229; planter der s&#229; vi pl&#248;yer litt i jorden-</p>
      <p end="00:35:57,537" begin="00:35:55,741">-slik at de kan vokse.</p>
      <p end="00:35:59,953" begin="00:35:57,537">Jeg trodde at hagearbeid var hardt arbeid, Meyer?</p>
      <p end="00:36:03,293" begin="00:35:59,953">- Det er jo det! Jeg gjorde mye av det tyngste...</p>
      <p end="00:36:05,045" begin="00:36:03,640">- N&#229;r du sprer gj&#248;dselet?</p>
      <p end="00:36:05,611" begin="00:36:05,045">- Ja!</p>
      <p end="00:36:06,348" begin="00:36:05,611">- Akkurat...</p>
      <p end="00:36:09,385" begin="00:36:06,348">- Som n&#229;r jeg gravde opp hele j&#230;vla plassen forrige h&#248;st.</p>
      <p end="00:36:14,271" begin="00:36:09,385">Jeg putter disse fr&#248;ene i bakken.</p>
      <p end="00:36:18,857" begin="00:36:14,271">Meyer? Vi skal tilbringe fire dager p&#229; <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Hawthorne Valley Farm</span>.</p>
      <p end="00:36:21,781" begin="00:36:18,857">Alt p&#229; den g&#229;rden blir resirkulert?</p>
      <p end="00:36:22,629" begin="00:36:21,781">- Ja!</p>
      <p end="00:36:23,907" begin="00:36:22,629">- Det er alt selvforsynt.</p>
      <p end="00:36:24,588" begin="00:36:23,907">- Ja!</p>
      <p end="00:36:25,263" begin="00:36:24,588">- Veldig bra.</p>
      <p end="00:36:28,349" begin="00:36:25,263">- Jeg ringte de, og hele familien... Jeg, Isabella og Michelle...</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p end="00:36:29,978" begin="00:36:28,349">Det blir p&#229; en m&#229;te v&#229;r ferietur.</p>
      <p end="00:36:31,081" begin="00:36:29,978">- Det h&#248;res bra ut!</p>
      <p end="00:36:32,415" begin="00:36:31,081">- Ja.</p>
      <p end="00:36:43,336" begin="00:36:32,415">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="00:36:46,711" begin="00:36:43,336">- [Michelle] Det f&#248;les som at vi m&#229; snakke om &#229; skaffe enda et barn.</p>
      <p end="00:36:48,850" begin="00:36:46,711">- [Colin] Jaha?</p>
      <p end="00:36:53,612" begin="00:36:50,543">- Men jeg vet at du ikke vil ha enda et barn.</p>
      <p end="00:36:59,646" begin="00:36:53,612">S&#229; jeg f&#248;ler at det betyr at vi ikke skal ha enda et barn.</p>
      <p end="00:37:03,580" begin="00:37:01,417">- Hmmm.</p>
      <p end="00:37:08,081" begin="00:37:04,845">Da vi fikk Isabella, f&#248;lte jeg at du virkelig ville ha barn-</p>
      <p end="00:37:10,748" begin="00:37:08,081">-og at det jeg var ute etter hadde blitt oppfylt.</p>
      <p end="00:37:13,226" begin="00:37:10,748">Jeg kunne ikke holde det fra deg-</p>
      <p end="00:37:15,723" begin="00:37:13,226">-og jeg var villig til &#229; ta det steget med deg-</p>
      <p end="00:37:18,878" begin="00:37:15,723">-fordi jeg f&#248;lte at... Jeg mener det er artig fordi vi har denne historien-</p>
      <p end="00:37:20,548" begin="00:37:18,898">-hvor jeg var redd for &#229; bli gift, ogs&#229;-</p>
      <p end="00:37:23,009" begin="00:37:20,548">-og jeg ville si til deg: "Gj&#248;r vi det rette?-</p>
      <p end="00:37:25,516" begin="00:37:23,009">-og du sa "Ja", og jeg stolte p&#229;...</p>
      <p end="00:37:29,081" begin="00:37:25,516">Jeg stolte p&#229; deg, og for meg er det helt klart det riktige.</p>
      <p end="00:37:31,588" begin="00:37:29,127">Men n&#229;r jeg tenker p&#229; et nytt barn...</p>
      <p end="00:37:32,563" begin="00:37:31,588">- Ja?</p>
      <p end="00:37:38,231" begin="00:37:32,563">Hvem sine karrierer st&#229;r p&#229; spill og m&#229; kanskje settes vekk?</p>
      <p end="00:37:40,536" begin="00:37:38,231">Fordi du har veldig mye &#229; gj&#248;re p&#229; jobb.</p>
      <p end="00:37:43,959" begin="00:37:40,536">Hvis vi hadde hatt enda et barn, ville du v&#230;rt villig til &#229; gi opp jobben?</p>
      <p end="00:37:47,820" begin="00:37:43,959">- Jeg trenger ikke, det er s&#229;... Jeg trenger ikke &#229; gi opp-</p>
      <p end="00:37:50,358" begin="00:37:47,820">-jobben for &#229; ha enda et barn.</p>
      <p end="00:37:53,137" begin="00:37:50,728">Jeg vet ikke helt hvorfor du tar... Det f&#248;les ikke som at jobben min-</p>
      <p end="00:37:56,370" begin="00:37:53,137">-har noe med dette &#229; gj&#248;re egentlig.</p>
      <p end="00:37:59,947" begin="00:37:56,370">- Det gj&#248;r det, fordi poenget er...</p>
      <p end="00:38:02,920" begin="00:37:59,947">Jeg vil vite om vi kommer til &#229; f&#229; enda et barn, ikke sant?</p>
      <p end="00:38:06,845" begin="00:38:02,920">Jeg vil ikke ha enda et barn, ok?</p>
      <p end="00:38:10,307" begin="00:38:06,845">Men f&#248;r vi begynner &#229; tenke p&#229; det-</p>
      <p end="00:38:12,733" begin="00:38:10,307">-s&#229; er det ikke s&#229; mye fleksibiliet i tidsplanen v&#229;r, ikke sant?</p>
      <p end="00:38:17,293" begin="00:38:12,733">S&#229; det jeg lurer p&#229; er hvor skal den fleksibiliteten komme ifra?</p>
      <p end="00:38:20,054" begin="00:38:17,293">- Den kommer fra meg!</p>
      <p end="00:38:29,962" begin="00:38:28,285">[D&#248;ren lukkes]</p>
      <p end="00:38:33,824" begin="00:38:32,718">- Okey.</p>
      <p end="00:38:36,488" begin="00:38:33,824">Jeg samler opp alle vaskemidlene vi har i huset.</p>
      <p end="00:38:39,541" begin="00:38:36,704">Vanlige vaskemidler inneholder mange typer kjemikalier-</p>
      <p end="00:38:40,888" begin="00:38:39,541">-som ikke er bra for oss.</p>
      <p end="00:38:42,378" begin="00:38:40,888">De er ikke bra for milj&#248;et heller.</p>
      <p end="00:38:47,306" begin="00:38:42,378">Det ender opp med at de g&#229;r i vasken og inn i vannforsyningen.</p>
      <p end="00:38:52,703" begin="00:38:47,306">Det vi har her er massevis av ting som blir markedsf&#248;rt-</p>
      <p end="00:38:58,035" begin="00:38:52,703">-som naturlig og ikke en fare for milj&#248;et-</p>
      <p end="00:39:01,455" begin="00:38:58,035">-fordi vi har drevet p&#229; med dette lenge n&#229;.</p>
      <p end="00:39:04,283" begin="00:39:01,455">De lar deg ikke fylle p&#229; flaskene igjen-</p>
      <p end="00:39:08,229" begin="00:39:04,283">-og vi bruker ikke engangsprodukter-</p>
      <p end="00:39:10,508" begin="00:39:08,229">-men folk sp&#248;r: "Hva med resirkulerbare produkter?"</p>
      <p end="00:39:15,562" begin="00:39:10,508">Men faktum er at resirkulering av plastikk-</p>
      <p end="00:39:16,769" begin="00:39:15,562">-er ikke s&#229; bra som man skal ha det til.</p>
      <p end="00:39:19,875" begin="00:39:16,769">Det er bedre enn ingenting, men det er fortsatt ikke helt perfekt.</p>
      <p end="00:39:22,994" begin="00:39:19,875">S&#229; folk kaller det heller "nedsirkulering" istedenfor resirkulering-</p>
      <p end="00:39:27,221" begin="00:39:22,994">-fordi det mister kvalitet hver gang og blir giftig til slutt.</p>
      <p end="00:39:31,249" begin="00:39:27,221">Siden vi har g&#229;tt tom for ting, s&#229; har jeg tatt vare p&#229; tomme flasker-</p>
      <p end="00:39:36,477" begin="00:39:31,249">-slik at vi kan putte hjemmelaget vaskemidler i flaskene.</p>
      <p end="00:39:39,287" begin="00:39:37,375">Alle v&#229;re vaskemidler kan lages fra dette.</p>
      <p end="00:39:47,217" begin="00:39:39,287">Hvit eddik, bakepulver, Castile-s&#229;pe og Borax.</p>
      <p end="00:39:51,871" begin="00:39:47,217">[Vann som renner]</p>
      <p end="00:39:53,377" begin="00:39:51,871">Jeg vet ikke. Hvordan kan man si helt sikkert at det er rent?</p>
      <p end="00:39:56,484" begin="00:39:53,377">Det f&#248;les ut som at vi bruker-</p>
      <p end="00:39:58,999" begin="00:39:56,484">-helt vanlig vaskemiddel.</p>
      <p end="00:40:07,336" begin="00:40:05,945">Kj&#230;re? Du vet hva jeg gj&#248;r n&#229;, ikke sant?</p>
      <p end="00:40:09,733" begin="00:40:07,336">Jeg kaster alt av kosmetisk produkter.</p>
      <p end="00:40:10,995" begin="00:40:09,733">Min kosmetikk?</p>
      <p end="00:40:12,456" begin="00:40:10,995">Er ikke det meningen da?</p>
      <p end="00:40:14,484" begin="00:40:12,456">Du mener min sminke og alt det?</p>
      <p end="00:40:18,165" begin="00:40:14,484">Jeg trodde det, men vet ikke. Hva skal du gj&#248;re med sminken din?</p>
      <p end="00:40:20,555" begin="00:40:18,165">Hva gj&#248;r du? Skal du bare kaste det?</p>
      <p end="00:40:21,506" begin="00:40:20,555">Nei. Jeg skulle ikke det.</p>
      <p end="00:40:24,617" begin="00:40:21,506">Jeg skulle bare putte det i denne boksen helt til vi er ferdige.</p>
      <p end="00:40:28,267" begin="00:40:25,478">- Okey. Bare si ifra.</p>
      <p end="00:40:30,755" begin="00:40:28,756">[Colin ler]</p>
      <p end="00:40:36,095" begin="00:40:30,815">Jeg kan ikke gj&#248;re det alene. Kan du hjelpe meg?</p>
      <p end="00:40:42,811" begin="00:40:40,834">[Flasker som klirrer]</p>
      <p end="00:40:48,877" begin="00:40:47,396">- Kj&#230;re!</p>
      <p end="00:40:49,484" begin="00:40:48,877">- Ja?</p>
      <p end="00:40:53,030" begin="00:40:49,484">- Bare la den flasken det st&#229;r "fersk" p&#229; ligge. Jeg tar meg av den.</p>
      <p end="00:40:55,610" begin="00:40:53,030">Jeg lot den ligge.</p>
      <p end="00:41:00,373" begin="00:40:57,657">- Den er tom.</p>
      <p end="00:41:01,752" begin="00:41:00,373">- Jeg vet. Jeg trenger den.</p>
      <p end="00:41:02,298" begin="00:41:01,752">[Isabella snakker]</p>
      <p end="00:41:03,782" begin="00:41:02,298">- Fordi du vet hva jeg skal gj&#248;re? Jeg lager shampo-</p>
      <p end="00:41:05,904" begin="00:41:03,782">-og putter det i den.</p>
      <p end="00:41:11,451" begin="00:41:09,258">For noen dager siden blogget jeg om det faktum-</p>
      <p end="00:41:13,359" begin="00:41:11,451">-at vi skal kvitte oss med str&#248;mmen-</p>
      <p end="00:41:15,566" begin="00:41:13,359">-og jeg spurte etter r&#229;d og laget en liste over ting-</p>
      <p end="00:41:20,219" begin="00:41:15,566">-jeg trenger hjelp med, og en av de tingene var klesvask.</p>
      <p end="00:41:23,749" begin="00:41:20,219">Noen sendte e-post og sa at de vasket kl&#230;r i badekaret-</p>
      <p end="00:41:26,944" begin="00:41:23,749">-og de bare gikk p&#229; det og det h&#248;rtes bra ut.</p>
      <p end="00:41:28,190" begin="00:41:26,959">[Vann som spruter]</p>
      <p end="00:41:29,779" begin="00:41:28,190">[Isabella snakker]</p>
      <p end="00:41:31,427" begin="00:41:29,779">Vi du ogs&#229; pr&#248;ve?</p>
      <p end="00:41:35,146" begin="00:41:31,427">[Vann som skvulper]</p>
      <p end="00:41:37,019" begin="00:41:35,146">N&#229; m&#229; du g&#229; bakover.</p>
      <p end="00:41:38,197" begin="00:41:37,019">[Latter]</p>
      <p end="00:41:39,723" begin="00:41:38,197">Mamma!</p>
      <p end="00:41:40,735" begin="00:41:39,723">(Isabella snakker]</p>
      <p end="00:41:41,864" begin="00:41:40,735">Vi vasker kl&#230;r.</p>
      <p end="00:41:43,908" begin="00:41:41,864">- Jeg vil pr&#248;ve alene.</p>
      <p end="00:41:49,191" begin="00:41:43,908">Vil du det? Men jeg er bekymret for at du faller. Ikke gj&#248;r det.</p>
      <p end="00:41:51,668" begin="00:41:49,191">- Hva bruker du som vaskemiddel?</p>
      <p end="00:41:55,360" begin="00:41:51,668">- Du vet, Castile... Oi! Hva var det jeg sa?</p>
      <p end="00:41:56,776" begin="00:41:55,360">[Latter]</p>
      <p end="00:41:57,670" begin="00:41:56,776">Jeg sa du ikke skulle falle.</p>
      <p end="00:41:58,954" begin="00:41:57,670">- Kj&#230;re, hva er det oppi der?</p>
      <p end="00:42:00,471" begin="00:41:58,954">- Castile-s&#229;pe og Borax.</p>
      <p end="00:42:01,949" begin="00:42:00,471">- Hva er Borax?</p>
      <p end="00:42:05,510" begin="00:42:01,949">- Det er bare naturlig vaskemiddel. Vil du ogs&#229; pr&#248;ve?</p>
      <p end="00:42:07,665" begin="00:42:05,510">- Ja.</p>
      <p end="00:42:09,656" begin="00:42:07,665">[Latter]</p>
      <p end="00:42:10,676" begin="00:42:09,656">- [Isabella] Jeg vasker kl&#230;r.</p>
      <p end="00:42:12,571" begin="00:42:10,676">- Det gj&#248;r du.</p>
      <p end="00:42:15,415" begin="00:42:13,249">P&#229; skolen kommer hun til &#229; v&#230;re helt...</p>
      <p end="00:42:16,790" begin="00:42:15,415">[Michelle ler]</p>
      <p end="00:42:18,832" begin="00:42:16,790">- [Gisper] Oi, det var kaldt!</p>
      <p end="00:42:20,509" begin="00:42:18,832">- Det har ligget her i tre timer.</p>
      <p end="00:42:22,854" begin="00:42:20,509">- Dette er ikke morsomt.</p>
      <p end="00:42:25,565" begin="00:42:22,854">- Kom igjen! Det er som &#229; knuse druer.</p>
      <p end="00:42:27,456" begin="00:42:25,565">Kom igjen n&#229;, barn. F&#229; det rent.</p>
      <p end="00:42:29,461" begin="00:42:27,456">Jeg tror hun er ute etter tr&#248;bbel.</p>
      <p end="00:42:30,921" begin="00:42:29,461">- Tr&#248;bbel? Hvorfor?</p>
      <p end="00:42:33,444" begin="00:42:30,921">Det er bare det hun er ute etter.</p>
      <p end="00:42:34,550" begin="00:42:33,444">- [Isabella] Klesvask!</p>
      <p end="00:42:38,133" begin="00:42:34,550">- [Sammen] Vi vasker kl&#230;r!</p>
      <p end="00:42:44,427" begin="00:42:38,133">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="00:42:46,998" begin="00:42:44,427">- [TV-vert] Noen av vennene dine mener du er gal.</p>
      <p end="00:42:48,424" begin="00:42:46,998">[Colin ler]</p>
      <p end="00:42:51,129" begin="00:42:48,424">- Og jeg pr&#248;ver &#229; forestille meg at n&#229;r de blir bedt p&#229; middag-</p>
      <p end="00:42:55,645" begin="00:42:51,129">-hos deg, s&#229; f&#229;r de pastinakk eller hva du har liggende rundt.</p>
      <p end="00:43:00,461" begin="00:42:55,900">Hva mener vennene dine om dette? Ingen servietter eller toalettpapir.</p>
      <p end="00:43:02,364" begin="00:43:00,461">Hadde du klart dette?</p>
      <p end="00:43:04,349" begin="00:43:02,364">[Publikum ler]</p>
      <p end="00:43:06,839" begin="00:43:04,349">- Ingen m&#229; gj&#248;re det jeg gj&#248;r. Det er ikke det viktigste.</p>
      <p end="00:43:09,530" begin="00:43:06,839">Det jeg gj&#248;r er &#229; gi problemet oppmerksomhet, men alle-</p>
      <p end="00:43:11,165" begin="00:43:09,530">-burde bare l&#230;re hva som er mulig &#229; gj&#248;re.</p>
      <p end="00:43:12,468" begin="00:43:11,165">- Du er n&#229; fem og en halv m&#229;ned inn i prosjektet.</p>
      <p end="00:43:15,195" begin="00:43:12,468">Neste steg er &#229; kvitte seg med str&#248;mmen-</p>
      <p end="00:43:18,160" begin="00:43:15,195">-og leve av dagslyset alene, i New York City?</p>
      <p end="00:43:20,128" begin="00:43:18,160">- Det er en bryter i min leilighet-</p>
      <p end="00:43:21,987" begin="00:43:20,128">-som er bryteren for hele komplekset.</p>
      <p end="00:43:25,931" begin="00:43:21,987">Vi har en liten fest med vennene v&#229;re og vi skal sl&#229; bryteren av.</p>
      <p end="00:43:26,735" begin="00:43:25,931">S&#229;, ja.</p>
      <p end="00:43:27,983" begin="00:43:26,735">- Vi skal la alle sammen f&#229; vite det.</p>
      <p end="00:43:31,594" begin="00:43:27,983">Vi skal f&#248;lge Colin gjennom dette lange &#229;ret.</p>
      <p end="00:43:35,861" begin="00:43:31,594">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="00:43:39,457" begin="00:43:35,861">- [Colin] Jeg skulle hente spinat, men n&#229; som str&#248;mmen g&#229;r ut-</p>
      <p end="00:43:41,453" begin="00:43:39,457">-innser jeg at jeg kan ikke kj&#248;pe s&#229; veldig mye.</p>
      <p end="00:43:44,147" begin="00:43:41,453">Jeg kan bare kj&#248;pe for de neste par dagene.</p>
      <p end="00:43:46,428" begin="00:43:44,147">Fordi bortsett fra det, s&#229; vil alt sammen bli d&#229;rlig.</p>
      <p end="00:43:59,083" begin="00:43:46,428">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="00:44:00,770" begin="00:43:59,083">- I kveld skrur vi av str&#248;mmen-</p>
      <p end="00:44:03,409" begin="00:44:00,770">-og jeg har ikke tenkt p&#229; det-</p>
      <p end="00:44:09,365" begin="00:44:03,409">-men jeg f&#248;ler vi beveger oss inn i den sjette m&#229;neden-</p>
      <p end="00:44:11,615" begin="00:44:09,365">-og jeg begynner &#229; forst&#229; utbyttet-</p>
      <p end="00:44:14,918" begin="00:44:11,615">-og fordelene begynner &#229; vise seg, s&#229; jeg er spent.</p>
      <p end="00:44:17,696" begin="00:44:14,918">Men jeg er sikker p&#229; at hvis du snakker med meg i morgen-</p>
      <p end="00:44:19,357" begin="00:44:17,696">-f&#248;ler jeg meg kanskje miserabel.</p>
      <p end="00:44:21,380" begin="00:44:19,357">La oss snakke litt om hvordan det kommer til &#229; bli.</p>
      <p end="00:44:23,510" begin="00:44:21,380">- Det kommer til &#229; v&#230;re en overgangsfase.</p>
      <p end="00:44:25,638" begin="00:44:23,510">Det er vanskelig som alt annet.</p>
      <p end="00:44:37,109" begin="00:44:25,638">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="00:44:38,126" begin="00:44:37,109">- Hei.</p>
      <p end="00:44:39,683" begin="00:44:38,126">Hei, Gracie!</p>
      <p end="00:44:41,328" begin="00:44:39,683">- Hvordan g&#229;r det?</p>
      <p end="00:44:41,329" begin="00:44:41,328">- Hei.</p>
      <p end="00:44:42,800" begin="00:44:41,329">- Hvordan g&#229;r det?<br/>- Bra.</p>
      <p end="00:44:44,438" begin="00:44:42,800">- Hei! Hvordan g&#229;r det?</p>
      <p end="00:44:48,200" begin="00:44:44,438">- [Mann] Forbrukere som resirkulerer hjelper oss med &#229; hjelpe planeten.</p>
      <p end="00:44:49,490" begin="00:44:48,200">Er det alt bra nok?</p>
      <p end="00:44:51,542" begin="00:44:49,490">[Latter]</p>
      <p end="00:44:54,395" begin="00:44:52,227">[Folk snakker]</p>
      <p end="00:44:55,503" begin="00:44:54,395">- [Kvinnelig gjest] Engangskoppen.</p>
      <p end="00:44:56,171" begin="00:44:55,503">- [Mannlig gjest] Ja.</p>
      <p end="00:45:01,827" begin="00:44:56,171">- Ikke-resirkulerbar kopp og en jakke og s&#229; har du to kopper som faktisk-</p>
      <p end="00:45:02,974" begin="00:45:01,827">-ser ut som det.</p>
      <p end="00:45:04,256" begin="00:45:02,974">Du har brutt hver eneste regel.</p>
      <p end="00:45:05,192" begin="00:45:04,256">- Okey.</p>
      <p end="00:45:09,485" begin="00:45:07,050">- [Michelle] Har dere sett v&#229;rt nye kj&#248;leskap?</p>
      <p end="00:45:10,599" begin="00:45:09,485">Du vil ha en, ikke sant?</p>
      <p end="00:45:11,253" begin="00:45:10,599">- [Kvinnelig gjest] Ja.</p>
      <p end="00:45:13,322" begin="00:45:11,253">- Hva er historien?</p>
      <p end="00:45:14,395" begin="00:45:13,322">Hva heter den?</p>
      <p end="00:45:15,635" begin="00:45:14,395">- [Colin] Den kalles en "Pot on Pot".</p>
      <p end="00:45:22,208" begin="00:45:15,635">Den er oppfunnet i Nigeria og id&#233;en er at vannet fordamper-</p>
      <p end="00:45:26,355" begin="00:45:22,208">-fra... Sanden mellom de to pottene er v&#229;t og vannet fordamper.</p>
      <p end="00:45:27,028" begin="00:45:26,355">- [Kvinnelig gjest] Okey.</p>
      <p end="00:45:29,956" begin="00:45:27,028">Og energien fra fordampingen er tatt fra den indre potten-</p>
