      <p end="00:58:30,625" begin="00:58:28,867">-min for en liten stund.</p>
      <p end="00:58:36,142" begin="00:58:30,625">Jeg vil ikke bruke all v&#229;r energi i "Pot in a Pot".</p>
      <p end="00:58:37,706" begin="00:58:36,142">Jeg vil ha enda et barn.</p>
      <p end="00:58:40,308" begin="00:58:37,706">Jeg vil ikke tilbringe ferien min p&#229; en g&#229;rd.</p>
      <p end="00:58:48,598" begin="00:58:40,308">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="00:58:49,575" begin="00:58:48,598">Da vi giftet oss-</p>
      <p end="00:58:52,159" begin="00:58:49,575">-tenkte jeg at jeg skulle gifte meg med Colin, men det var en ting.</p>
      <p end="00:58:55,542" begin="00:58:52,159">Jeg liker ikke camping. Det blir jeg ikke med p&#229;.</p>
      <p end="00:58:58,964" begin="00:58:55,542">Men n&#229; har hele huset v&#229;rt blitt til en campingplass.</p>
      <p end="00:59:01,478" begin="00:58:58,964">Jeg liker heller ikke naturen.</p>
      <p end="00:59:04,213" begin="00:59:01,478">Og i ferien skal vi ut i naturen.</p>
      <p end="00:59:05,685" begin="00:59:04,213">[Latter]</p>
      <p end="00:59:10,499" begin="00:59:08,016">Vi skal se p&#229; og jobbe med all den maten som vi spiser.</p>
      <p end="00:59:13,059" begin="00:59:10,499">Dette er hvor maten fra markedet kommer fra.</p>
      <p end="00:59:20,095" begin="00:59:13,059">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="00:59:23,134" begin="00:59:20,095">- Hei, ku.</p>
      <p end="00:59:25,535" begin="00:59:23,134">- Du kan strekke ut h&#229;nden og ta p&#229; den.</p>
      <p end="00:59:27,246" begin="00:59:25,535">- Hei, ku.</p>
      <p end="00:59:29,210" begin="00:59:27,246">- Takk for at vi fikk komme.</p>
      <p end="00:59:29,921" begin="00:59:29,210">Takk.</p>
      <p end="00:59:30,746" begin="00:59:29,921">- [Rachel Schneider] Velkommen!</p>
      <p end="00:59:32,243" begin="00:59:30,746">Jeg har den beste &#248;kten allerede.</p>
      <p end="00:59:33,181" begin="00:59:32,243">Vi har bare v&#230;rt her i en time.</p>
      <p end="00:59:34,310" begin="00:59:33,181">- Ja.</p>
      <p end="00:59:43,918" begin="00:59:40,250">- [Rachel] Idet du jobber med dette-</p>
      <p end="00:59:52,434" begin="00:59:43,918">-dyrker du en veldig vital og dynamisk skapning som er i balanse.</p>
      <p end="00:59:54,787" begin="00:59:52,434">Det er en lukket l&#248;kke.</p>
      <p end="00:59:57,290" begin="00:59:54,787">Kyrne eter gresset.</p>
      <p end="01:00:02,673" begin="00:59:57,290">De gir deg melk, men de gir deg ogs&#229; gj&#248;dsel.</p>
      <p end="01:00:05,973" begin="01:00:02,673">Gj&#248;dselet blir kompostert. Det er det som er fruktbarheten.</p>
      <p end="01:00:11,223" begin="01:00:05,973">Vi lager cirka 400 tonn med kompost hvert &#229;r.</p>
      <p end="01:00:13,367" begin="01:00:11,223">Lukt.</p>
      <p end="01:00:14,544" begin="01:00:13,367">- Ja. Det lukter som jord.</p>
      <p end="01:00:16,546" begin="01:00:14,544">Det lukter som markebingen min egentlig.</p>
      <p end="01:00:23,558" begin="01:00:18,784">- Du sier alts&#229; at dette er realiseringen av hans verdier?</p>
      <p end="01:00:24,913" begin="01:00:23,558">- Ja.</p>
      <p end="01:00:28,782" begin="01:00:24,913">- Hvordan f&#248;les det n&#229; seks m&#229;neder uti det?</p>
      <p end="01:00:30,658" begin="01:00:28,782">- Det er for seint &#229; snu.</p>
      <p end="01:00:32,342" begin="01:00:30,658">- Det er ingen vei tilbake, alts&#229;.</p>
      <p end="01:00:33,939" begin="01:00:32,342">Akkurat.</p>
      <p end="01:00:35,660" begin="01:00:33,939">- Dette er for familien v&#229;r.</p>
      <p end="01:00:37,605" begin="01:00:35,660">Det handler ikke bare om prosjektet.</p>
      <p end="01:00:41,908" begin="01:00:40,894">- [Mann] Hvor er du ifra?</p>
      <p end="01:00:45,084" begin="01:00:41,908">- [Colin] Jeg bor i byen. Jeg h&#229;per jeg hjelper istedenfor &#229; v&#230;re til hinder.</p>
      <p end="01:00:47,904" begin="01:00:45,084">[Latter]</p>
      <p end="01:00:49,061" begin="01:00:47,904">- [Mannlig g&#229;rdbruker] Da g&#229;r vi.</p>
      <p end="01:00:52,780" begin="01:00:49,061">[Bjeller klinger]</p>
      <p end="01:00:54,546" begin="01:00:52,780">- [Mann] Det er Henry. Han er okse.</p>
      <p end="01:00:56,914" begin="01:00:54,546">Kom igjen, Henry. Da kj&#248;rer vi.</p>
      <p end="01:00:59,230" begin="01:00:56,914">Vi m&#229; eskortere Henry inn i l&#229;ven.</p>
      <p end="01:01:00,218" begin="01:00:59,230">[Ku m&#248;er]</p>
      <p end="01:01:01,529" begin="01:01:00,218">- [Michelle] Natten f&#248;r vi dro-</p>
      <p end="01:01:04,134" begin="01:01:01,529">-hadde bonden og Colin en samtale.</p>
      <p end="01:01:07,509" begin="01:01:04,134">De snakket om hvordan dalen en gang var full av sauer.</p>
      <p end="01:01:10,159" begin="01:01:07,509">De snakket ogs&#229; om hvordan folk-</p>
      <p end="01:01:13,930" begin="01:01:10,159">-kan bli til dyr.</p>
      <p end="01:01:18,429" begin="01:01:13,930">Jeg ble betatt av den samtalen.</p>
      <p end="01:01:29,319" begin="01:01:26,676">S&#229; gikk jeg og la meg med den vakre g&#229;rdsluften-</p>
      <p end="01:01:32,838" begin="01:01:29,319">-i det vakre huset med disse vakre menneskene-</p>
      <p end="01:01:35,514" begin="01:01:32,838">-som behandlet oss som vi var familie-</p>
      <p end="01:01:38,936" begin="01:01:35,514">-og jeg dr&#248;mte at jeg var en av sauene.</p>
      <p end="01:01:41,252" begin="01:01:38,936">Det er rart fordi besteforeldrene mine var g&#229;rdbrukere-</p>
      <p end="01:01:44,946" begin="01:01:41,252">De var selvforsynt, og jeg f&#248;lte at...</p>
      <p end="01:01:49,148" begin="01:01:44,946">Jeg f&#248;lte at de etterlot seg noe.</p>
      <p end="01:01:53,606" begin="01:01:49,148">Og jeg f&#248;lte at jeg m&#229;tte tilbake og hente det.</p>
      <p end="01:01:57,443" begin="01:01:54,560">Da jeg h&#248;rte bonden snakke om flokken-</p>
      <p end="01:01:59,437" begin="01:01:57,443">-og hvordan noe kan skje en av kyrne-</p>
      <p end="01:02:02,169" begin="01:01:59,437">-men at flokken g&#229;r videre...</p>
      <p end="01:02:04,820" begin="01:02:02,169">Det f&#248;ltes som at jeg v&#229;knet opp.</p>
      <p end="01:02:09,088" begin="01:02:04,820">Det f&#248;ltes som at jeg m&#229; gjenforenes med noe.</p>
      <p end="01:02:17,610" begin="01:02:13,827">[Horn bl&#229;ses]</p>
      <p end="01:02:31,915" begin="01:02:24,221">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="01:02:35,708" begin="01:02:31,915">Et selskap l&#229;nte meg dette solcellepanelet for dette prosjektet.</p>
      <p end="01:02:40,294" begin="01:02:35,708">Jeg kan endre m&#229;ten str&#248;m blir levert til huset mitt.</p>
      <p end="01:02:41,742" begin="01:02:40,294">- Har du den?<br/>- Ja.</p>
      <p end="01:02:45,200" begin="01:02:42,665">Solcellepanelet gir nok str&#248;m-</p>
      <p end="01:02:48,582" begin="01:02:45,200">-til at jeg kan bruke datamaskinen og blogge.</p>
      <p end="01:02:53,987" begin="01:02:51,137">Men det som er interessant med denne fasen er at-</p>
      <p end="01:02:56,873" begin="01:02:53,987">-det handler ikke om &#229; bruke s&#229; lite-</p>
      <p end="01:02:59,105" begin="01:02:56,873">-som vi muligens kan bruke-</p>
      <p end="01:03:04,611" begin="01:02:59,105">-men &#229; finne ut hvordan jeg f&#229;r tak i det jeg trenger p&#229; en b&#230;rekraftig m&#229;te.</p>
      <p end="01:03:07,768" begin="01:03:05,381">Og dette m&#229; vi klare oss med; str&#248;mmen-</p>
      <p end="01:03:09,339" begin="01:03:07,768">-og solcellepanelet.</p>
      <p end="01:03:11,643" begin="01:03:09,339">Men det er ogs&#229; det vi m&#229; gj&#248;re med v&#229;re systemer.</p>
      <p end="01:03:14,452" begin="01:03:11,643">Vi trenger bare &#229; finne ut hvordan vi f&#229;r tak i ting som folk trenger-</p>
      <p end="01:03:17,292" begin="01:03:14,452">-uten at det g&#229;r utover planeten.</p>
      <p end="01:03:20,419" begin="01:03:17,292">[Taster]</p>
      <p end="01:03:32,474" begin="01:03:29,282">Fortell han at han skal komme seg ut av sykkelfilen.</p>
      <p end="01:03:38,053" begin="01:03:33,853">Vil du vite hva hun fikk som gave til 40-&#229;rsdagen?</p>
      <p end="01:03:39,871" begin="01:03:38,763">Ingen prevensjon.</p>
      <p end="01:03:42,687" begin="01:03:39,871">Du vet hva jeg mener?</p>
      <p end="01:03:46,029" begin="01:03:42,687">Vi kaller det russisk rulett.</p>
      <p end="01:03:49,037" begin="01:03:46,029">- N&#229; er sp&#248;rsm&#229;let: er det klikk-klikk eller pang-pang?</p>
      <p end="01:03:53,059" begin="01:03:49,037">- Hvis det er pang-pang, da d&#248;r jeg og hun overlever.</p>
      <p end="01:04:00,253" begin="01:03:57,289">Se opp for en tulling p&#229; din h&#248;yre side.</p>
      <p end="01:04:06,366" begin="01:04:01,455">Blogginnlegget mitt i dag handlet om muligheter i en krisesituasjon.</p>
      <p end="01:04:09,190" begin="01:04:06,366">Forestill deg at vi gjorde byen til et fint sted &#229; leve.</p>
      <p end="01:04:12,943" begin="01:04:09,190">S&#229; de to kommentarene s&#229; langt er...</p>
      <p end="01:04:15,084" begin="01:04:12,943">La oss v&#230;re realistiske.</p>
      <p end="01:04:19,069" begin="01:04:15,084">Du kan ikke gj&#248;re byen et fint sted, s&#229; bare glem det.</p>
      <p end="01:04:23,001" begin="01:04:19,069">Det er mangel p&#229; idealisme, men jeg tror realisme brakte oss dit vi er n&#229;.</p>
      <p end="01:04:24,305" begin="01:04:23,001">Skj&#248;nner du?</p>
      <p end="01:04:26,171" begin="01:04:24,305">[Horn tuter]</p>
      <p end="01:04:27,013" begin="01:04:26,171">- Det hjelper.</p>
      <p end="01:04:32,717" begin="01:04:31,239">G&#229;r det bra, Michelle?</p>
      <p end="01:04:37,306" begin="01:04:36,462">- Pass p&#229;, kj&#230;re.</p>
      <p end="01:04:39,055" begin="01:04:37,306">- Jeg vet.</p>
      <p end="01:04:43,285" begin="01:04:42,199">- Det er s&#229; stille.</p>
      <p end="01:04:44,850" begin="01:04:43,285">- Jeg vet.</p>
      <p end="01:04:50,832" begin="01:04:49,348">- Er det Fort Tilden der borte?</p>
      <p end="01:04:52,264" begin="01:04:50,832">- Ja.</p>
      <p end="01:04:57,329" begin="01:04:55,165">- Herregud, dette er som Hamptons.</p>
      <p end="01:04:58,786" begin="01:04:57,329">- Det er bedre enn det.</p>
      <p end="01:05:00,541" begin="01:04:58,786">- Fordi det er ingen her.</p>
      <p end="01:05:03,340" begin="01:05:01,617">[Colin ler]</p>
      <p end="01:05:08,876" begin="01:05:04,048">- Herregud, hvor radikalt er dette?</p>
      <p end="01:05:12,632" begin="01:05:08,876">Og dette er fortsatt New York City.</p>
      <p end="01:05:14,361" begin="01:05:12,632">- Oi, insekt!</p>
      <p end="01:05:18,128" begin="01:05:14,928">- Skal vi ta en dukkert?</p>
      <p end="01:05:21,317" begin="01:05:19,308">- Tja...</p>
      <p end="01:05:24,749" begin="01:05:21,496">[B&#248;lgeskvulp]</p>
      <p end="01:05:26,542" begin="01:05:24,749">- Det er utrolig hvor hardf&#248;r naturen er.</p>
      <p end="01:05:28,250" begin="01:05:26,542">Det er vadere p&#229; denne stranden-</p>
      <p end="01:05:30,253" begin="01:05:28,250">-og alle sammen pr&#248;ver &#229; overleve.</p>
      <p end="01:05:34,040" begin="01:05:30,253">Og s&#229; har man disse krabbene som er i New York City.</p>
      <p end="01:05:36,118" begin="01:05:34,040">Ser du to stykker?</p>
      <p end="01:05:36,666" begin="01:05:36,118">- Ja.</p>
      <p end="01:05:37,808" begin="01:05:36,666">- Vent litt.</p>
      <p end="01:05:38,381" begin="01:05:37,808">- Joda, jeg ser de.</p>
      <p end="01:05:41,132" begin="01:05:38,381">[B&#248;lgeskvulp]</p>
      <p end="01:05:43,564" begin="01:05:42,075">- Folk kan snakke om-</p>
      <p end="01:05:47,998" begin="01:05:43,564">-hva som er det vanskeligste. G&#229;r man tom for ting?</p>
      <p end="01:05:50,793" begin="01:05:47,998">Alle aspektene med dette prosjektet er vanskelig.</p>
      <p end="01:05:52,738" begin="01:05:50,793">Men det handler ikke om &#229; g&#229; tom for ting.</p>
      <p end="01:05:55,193" begin="01:05:52,738">Det handler ikke om at jeg ikke tar vare p&#229; meg selv.</p>
      <p end="01:05:56,328" begin="01:05:55,193">Det er det motsatte.</p>
      <p end="01:05:57,827" begin="01:05:56,328">Det handler om &#229; se-</p>
      <p end="01:06:03,231" begin="01:05:57,827">-om det g&#229;r an &#229; leve et godt liv uten &#229; sl&#248;se s&#229; f&#230;lt.</p>
      <p end="01:06:09,606" begin="01:06:03,231">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="01:06:10,990" begin="01:06:09,606">- Colin m&#248;tte en fantastisk kvinne-</p>
      <p end="01:06:14,391" begin="01:06:10,990">-p&#229; markedet, som l&#229;nte oss sin trehjulssykkel.</p>
      <p end="01:06:17,899" begin="01:06:14,391">Dette forandret alt.</p>
      <p end="01:06:25,851" begin="01:06:21,851">Vi har ikke TV, lys, str&#248;m eller air-condition.</p>
      <p end="01:06:29,164" begin="01:06:25,851">Det var alt dette som holdt oss innend&#248;rs.</p>
      <p end="01:06:31,867" begin="01:06:29,164">Vi blir tvunget ut av leiligheten n&#229; for tiden.</p>
      <p end="01:06:34,490" begin="01:06:31,867">[Vannskvulp]</p>
      <p end="01:06:38,103" begin="01:06:34,490">Det kjennes ut som at dagene varer evig.</p>
      <p end="01:06:43,010" begin="01:06:41,253">- Hva er de?</p>
      <p end="01:06:45,449" begin="01:06:43,010">- Det er ildfluer.</p>
      <p end="01:06:47,447" begin="01:06:45,449">- [Isabella] Det er et lys.</p>
      <p end="01:06:51,562" begin="01:06:48,839">[Isabella hyler]</p>
      <p end="01:06:52,796" begin="01:06:51,562">- Oi, oi, oi, oi!</p>
      <p end="01:06:56,496" begin="01:06:54,235">[Colin ler]</p>
      <p end="01:07:00,338" begin="01:06:58,081">- Spiller dere <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Gin Rummy?</span></p>
      <p end="01:07:02,074" begin="01:07:00,338">- Ja, det gj&#248;r vi.</p>
      <p end="01:07:03,938" begin="01:07:02,074">- Jeg vil vise deg noe. Greit?</p>
      <p end="01:07:10,109" begin="01:07:03,938">Dette kalles &#229; sparke pappa i baken, ikke sant?</p>
      <p end="01:07:15,229" begin="01:07:12,448">- [Meyer] Vi kommer fra helt forskjellige omr&#229;der.</p>
      <p end="01:07:23,821" begin="01:07:15,229">Ingen kommer til &#229; v&#230;re s&#229; naive-</p>
      <p end="01:07:27,177" begin="01:07:23,821">-som vi var p&#229; slutten av 60-tallet.</p>
      <p end="01:07:29,981" begin="01:07:27,177">- Men jeg tror det er noe av det samme-</p>
      <p end="01:07:34,037" begin="01:07:29,981">-men mer dempet, som skjer n&#229; for tiden. Ikke helt det samme-</p>
      <p end="01:07:41,574" begin="01:07:34,037">-men jeg f&#248;ler det er en stille revolusjon som er i ferd med &#229; skje.</p>
      <p end="01:07:46,488" begin="01:07:41,574">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="01:07:48,876" begin="01:07:46,488">- [Meyer] Det andre som er viktig er dette...</p>
      <p end="01:07:55,913" begin="01:07:51,963">Denne kalles <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Scape.</span> S-C-A-P-E.</p>
      <p end="01:08:00,006" begin="01:07:55,913">Jeg foresl&#229;r at du tar med deg en eller to hjem.</p>
      <p end="01:08:00,901" begin="01:08:00,006">- Okey.</p>
      <p end="01:08:02,711" begin="01:08:00,901">- Dette er b&#248;nnene.</p>
      <p end="01:08:06,039" begin="01:08:02,711">Du kan se hvordan de tar tak i stangen.</p>
      <p end="01:08:07,281" begin="01:08:06,039">Ser du dette?</p>
      <p end="01:08:07,827" begin="01:08:07,281">-Ja.</p>
      <p end="01:08:10,740" begin="01:08:07,827">- Det dukker opp tomater snart.</p>
      <p end="01:08:20,629" begin="01:08:17,013">- Er du generelt sett optimistisk ang&#229;ende menneskeheten eller skeptisk?</p>
      <p end="01:08:24,273" begin="01:08:20,629">- Det er alltid halvt om halvt.</p>
      <p end="01:08:25,775" begin="01:08:24,273">- Akkurat.</p>
      <p end="01:08:29,571" begin="01:08:25,775">- Man vet at noe blir bedre, mens-</p>
      <p end="01:08:31,925" begin="01:08:29,571">-noe blir bare v&#230;rre.</p>
      <p end="01:08:35,777" begin="01:08:33,448">- Ja.</p>
      <p end="01:08:37,025" begin="01:08:35,777">- Selv om alt dette...</p>
      <p end="01:08:38,685" begin="01:08:37,025">Hver gang man pr&#248;ver &#229; gj&#248;re noe riktig-</p>
      <p end="01:08:45,475" begin="01:08:38,685">-uansett hvilket niv&#229; man er p&#229;, s&#229; er det alltid noe uforutsett.</p>
      <p end="01:08:51,940" begin="01:08:46,675">Jeg tror prosjektet gj&#248;r det mulig for folk &#229; narre seg selv.</p>
      <p end="01:08:55,346" begin="01:08:51,940">At alt de trenger &#229; gj&#248;re er &#229; bytte lysp&#230;ren-</p>
      <p end="01:08:58,948" begin="01:08:55,346">-og resirkulere posene.</p>
      <p end="01:09:04,265" begin="01:08:58,948">S&#229; lenge de f&#248;ler at det er s&#229;nn, kommer ingen politiker til &#229; bite p&#229; kroken.</p>
      <p end="01:09:10,124" begin="01:09:04,265">- Og jeg tror det er sant, at det er... Det er b&#229;de og.</p>
      <p end="01:09:12,317" begin="01:09:10,124">Man m&#229; ha...</p>
      <p end="01:09:14,168" begin="01:09:12,317">Jeg tror det er...</p>
      <p end="01:09:17,005" begin="01:09:14,168">Hvis man st&#229;r et sted politisk, da er det integritet til-</p>
      <p end="01:09:19,837" begin="01:09:17,005">-&#229; leve p&#229; en m&#229;te som reflekterer det politiske standpunktet.</p>
      <p end="01:09:22,651" begin="01:09:20,875">- Med den risikoen for at det blir altfor personlig.</p>
      <p end="01:09:23,647" begin="01:09:22,651">- Akkurat.</p>
      <p end="01:09:27,370" begin="01:09:23,647">- Men, du vet, det er bare fakta.</p>
