      <p end="01:20:33,847" begin="01:20:32,746">- Ingen &#229;rsak.</p>
      <p end="01:20:35,409" begin="01:20:33,847">- Fordi det gir oss et godt...</p>
      <p end="01:20:37,182" begin="01:20:35,409">- Det gir oss noe &#229; g&#229; p&#229;.</p>
      <p end="01:20:40,439" begin="01:20:37,182">- Det &#229; bruke mindre er en start, men det er ikke nok.</p>
      <p end="01:20:45,750" begin="01:20:40,439">Vi m&#229; kreve at systemene blir b&#230;rekraftige.</p>
      <p end="01:20:51,892" begin="01:20:48,801">- Du kan vugge den. Jeg vugger den, okey?</p>
      <p end="01:20:54,570" begin="01:20:51,892">Vil du vugge mens du ser p&#229; Frankie?</p>
      <p end="01:20:58,479" begin="01:20:54,570">- Vi sa til Isabella at vi trodde Michelle hadde en baby i magen-</p>
      <p end="01:21:00,718" begin="01:20:58,479">-men vi tok feil.</p>
      <p end="01:21:02,930" begin="01:21:00,718">Hun hadde faktisk ikke det.</p>
      <p end="01:21:04,042" begin="01:21:02,930">- Den andre...</p>
      <p end="01:21:06,202" begin="01:21:04,042">Jeg tror det var den andre gangen jeg bes&#248;kte legen.</p>
      <p end="01:21:08,470" begin="01:21:06,202">F&#248;rste gang vi var til legen, var alt ok.</p>
      <p end="01:21:11,916" begin="01:21:08,470">Men den andre gangen vi var til legen-</p>
      <p end="01:21:13,624" begin="01:21:11,916">-var det ingen hjerteslag.</p>
      <p end="01:21:16,062" begin="01:21:14,793">- Ja.</p>
      <p end="01:21:18,847" begin="01:21:16,062">Det var ingen hjerteslag.</p>
      <p end="01:21:25,801" begin="01:21:22,323">- Hvor skal du n&#229;, da?</p>
      <p end="01:21:34,303" begin="01:21:32,582">Fra historiens perspektiv-</p>
      <p end="01:21:36,154" begin="01:21:34,303">-s&#229; ville det ha v&#230;rt en perfekt slutt p&#229; historien.</p>
      <p end="01:21:40,690" begin="01:21:36,154">Jeg skled over-</p>
      <p end="01:21:43,086" begin="01:21:40,690">-til <span tts:fontStyle="italic">No Impact</span> og omfavnet det-</p>
      <p end="01:21:44,941" begin="01:21:43,086">-og det var det Colin ville.</p>
      <p end="01:21:48,241" begin="01:21:44,941">S&#229; ble jeg gravid, og det var det jeg egentlig ville-</p>
      <p end="01:21:49,857" begin="01:21:48,241">-og s&#229; slynger prosjektet seg ned.</p>
      <p end="01:21:52,283" begin="01:21:49,857">Det er alt i en bue.</p>
      <p end="01:21:58,342" begin="01:21:52,283">Men det er ikke en bue; det er en diger, l&#248;s tr&#229;d.</p>
      <p end="01:22:01,544" begin="01:21:58,342">En l&#248;s tr&#229;d.</p>
      <p end="01:22:07,152" begin="01:22:01,544">Det er en fortellende og &#229;ndelig l&#248;s tr&#229;d.</p>
      <p end="01:22:14,081" begin="01:22:07,152">Bare en l&#248;s tr&#229;d. Det er mange av de i livet.</p>
      <p end="01:22:16,664" begin="01:22:14,081">- Jeg tror vi pr&#248;ver igjen.</p>
      <p end="01:22:21,203" begin="01:22:18,862">- De er som regnbuer.</p>
      <p end="01:22:23,266" begin="01:22:21,203">- Er det regnbuer p&#229; f&#248;ttene dine?</p>
      <p end="01:22:25,412" begin="01:22:23,266">- [Isabella] Regnbuef&#248;tter.</p>
      <p end="01:22:32,366" begin="01:22:30,271">- [Meyer] "Svanesang" h&#248;res i hagen n&#229;r-</p>
      <p end="01:22:35,125" begin="01:22:32,366">-man snur om jorden p&#229; h&#248;sten.</p>
      <p end="01:22:39,816" begin="01:22:35,125">Da er sesongen over.</p>
      <p end="01:22:44,166" begin="01:22:43,111">- Det er interessant-</p>
      <p end="01:22:46,059" begin="01:22:44,166">-fordi vi har returnert til maten vi spiste-</p>
      <p end="01:22:47,426" begin="01:22:46,059">-da prosjektet startet.</p>
      <p end="01:22:51,833" begin="01:22:47,426">Alt er squash, rotgr&#248;nnsaker og s&#229;nne ting.</p>
      <p end="01:22:55,259" begin="01:22:51,833">Og hagen blir snudd om p&#229;.</p>
      <p end="01:22:58,522" begin="01:22:55,259">S&#229; man...</p>
      <p end="01:23:02,767" begin="01:22:58,522">Det er ikke som n&#229;r man blar om p&#229; kalenderen og ser at et &#229;r har g&#229;tt.</p>
      <p end="01:23:06,691" begin="01:23:02,767">Man f&#248;ler at et &#229;r har g&#229;tt, fordi man gjenkjenner-</p>
      <p end="01:23:11,516" begin="01:23:06,691">-noe ved jorden.</p>
      <p end="01:23:13,212" begin="01:23:11,516">Vi er s&#229; usynkronisert i byen-</p>
      <p end="01:23:15,588" begin="01:23:13,212">-med alle de naturlige rytmene.</p>
      <p end="01:23:16,790" begin="01:23:15,588">Jeg visste ikke om dette f&#248;r-</p>
      <p end="01:23:19,045" begin="01:23:16,790">-men det er en glede &#229; v&#230;re forbundet med det.</p>
      <p end="01:23:41,023" begin="01:23:19,045">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="01:23:43,331" begin="01:23:41,023">- Det er iskaldt her.</p>
      <p end="01:23:51,051" begin="01:23:45,783">Datoen er syvende november, vi er nesten ferdige og jeg fryser.</p>
      <p end="01:23:52,651" begin="01:23:51,051">S&#229; det jeg bruker &#229; gj&#248;re...</p>
      <p end="01:23:55,434" begin="01:23:52,651">La oss si at jeg kommer hjem fra jobben, jeg har p&#229; en drakt-</p>
      <p end="01:24:00,931" begin="01:23:55,434">-men jeg kommer hit og varmer meg.</p>
      <p end="01:24:05,413" begin="01:24:00,931">Jeg varmer meg under dyna mange ganger n&#229;r det er kaldt.</p>
      <p end="01:24:06,789" begin="01:24:05,413">Vi mener ikke at det er over.</p>
      <p end="01:24:07,651" begin="01:24:06,789">Det er litt morsomt fordi-</p>
      <p end="01:24:09,115" begin="01:24:07,651">-vi skal v&#230;re atskilt n&#229;r det slutter.</p>
      <p end="01:24:10,897" begin="01:24:09,115">N&#229;r det slutter, for meg-</p>
      <p end="01:24:12,569" begin="01:24:10,897">-s&#229; skal jeg ta fly for &#229; bes&#248;ke foreldrene mine-</p>
      <p end="01:24:15,242" begin="01:24:12,569">-som jeg ikke har sett p&#229; et &#229;r.</p>
      <p end="01:24:18,276" begin="01:24:15,242">Colin blir v&#230;rende, men jeg tar med Isabella.</p>
      <p end="01:24:26,095" begin="01:24:18,276">Det er rart at vi ikke har snakket om det.</p>
      <p end="01:24:28,838" begin="01:24:26,095">Men alle p&#229; utsiden sp&#248;r meg om det.</p>
      <p end="01:24:30,554" begin="01:24:28,838">- Mamma?</p>
      <p end="01:24:32,826" begin="01:24:30,554">- Hva skjer, s&#248;tnos?</p>
      <p end="01:24:36,951" begin="01:24:32,826">- Det er ikke lys her. Jeg kan ikke se.</p>
      <p end="01:24:40,123" begin="01:24:36,951">- Jeg ser frem til &#229; lese i sengen med Isabella-</p>
      <p end="01:24:45,872" begin="01:24:40,123">-med rikelig belysning.</p>
      <p end="01:24:52,487" begin="01:24:51,182">Er du tr&#248;tt?</p>
      <p end="01:24:54,089" begin="01:24:52,487">- Nei.</p>
      <p end="01:24:57,991" begin="01:24:54,089">- Neste uke skjer det noe p&#229; universitetet.</p>
      <p end="01:25:02,408" begin="01:24:57,991">200 studenter skal pr&#248;ve p&#229; det samme som vi gjorde.</p>
      <p end="01:25:03,542" begin="01:25:02,408">- Det er s&#229; kult.</p>
      <p end="01:25:04,220" begin="01:25:03,542">- Ja.</p>
      <p end="01:25:08,887" begin="01:25:04,220">S&#229; jeg drar p&#229; s&#248;ndagen og forklarer hvordan det skal gj&#248;res.</p>
      <p end="01:25:14,012" begin="01:25:08,887">Og mandagen deretter skal jeg holde et foredrag.</p>
      <p end="01:25:21,216" begin="01:25:14,012">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="01:25:22,977" begin="01:25:21,216">Rom 206.</p>
      <p end="01:25:29,577" begin="01:25:25,321">Under eksperimentet vil dere oppdage at det ikke er s&#229; galt.</p>
      <p end="01:25:31,702" begin="01:25:29,577">Mitt eksperiment har bare to uker igjen.</p>
      <p end="01:25:33,497" begin="01:25:31,702">N&#229;r jeg n&#229; kommer ut av det ekstreme-</p>
      <p end="01:25:35,259" begin="01:25:33,497">-vil noe av det vi har gitt opp-</p>
      <p end="01:25:37,291" begin="01:25:35,259">-bli tatt tilbake igjen, men faktum er at vi balanserer-</p>
      <p end="01:25:39,624" begin="01:25:37,291">-ved at vi kommer til &#229; kraftig-</p>
      <p end="01:25:42,850" begin="01:25:39,624">-for&#229;rsake mindre p&#229;virkning p&#229; milj&#248;et-</p>
      <p end="01:25:47,267" begin="01:25:42,850">-og uten &#229; p&#229;virke hum&#248;ret v&#229;rt.</p>
      <p end="01:25:50,253" begin="01:25:47,267">Faktum er at hvis bare jeg endrer meg-</p>
      <p end="01:25:51,965" begin="01:25:50,253">-kommer det til &#229; v&#230;re ubetydelig.</p>
      <p end="01:25:56,052" begin="01:25:51,965">Men h&#229;pet er at hvis vi alle endrer oss-</p>
      <p end="01:25:59,149" begin="01:25:56,052">-kommer det til &#229; inspirere alle til &#229; endre seg.</p>
      <p end="01:26:03,819" begin="01:25:59,149">Den mest radikale, politiske handlingen man kan gj&#248;re er &#229; v&#230;re en optimist.</p>
      <p end="01:26:06,732" begin="01:26:03,819">Det mest radikale, politiske handlingen er &#229; tro hvis jeg endrer meg-</p>
      <p end="01:26:08,262" begin="01:26:06,732">-kommer andre til &#229; f&#248;lge etter.</p>
      <p end="01:26:13,146" begin="01:26:08,262">Grunnen til at jeg er her, er fordi en f&#248;rsteklassing ved navn Olive-</p>
      <p end="01:26:16,950" begin="01:26:13,146">-skrev p&#229; bloggen min og spurte om jeg kunne komme.</p>
      <p end="01:26:20,625" begin="01:26:16,950">Folk sp&#248;r meg hva ville jeg ha gjort hvis jeg kunne gj&#248;re en ting.</p>
      <p end="01:26:24,140" begin="01:26:20,625">Jeg hadde ikke brukt plastikkposer eller plastikkopper.</p>
      <p end="01:26:27,985" begin="01:26:24,940">Hvis det var bare en ting &#229; gj&#248;re-</p>
      <p end="01:26:31,034" begin="01:26:27,985">-ville det ha v&#230;rt &#229; melde seg frivillig inn i en milj&#248;vernorganisasjon.</p>
      <p end="01:26:33,949" begin="01:26:31,034">Delvis p&#229; grunn av at det er et samfunn.</p>
      <p end="01:26:38,565" begin="01:26:33,949">Jeg tror milj&#248;problemene har oppst&#229;tt-</p>
      <p end="01:26:41,074" begin="01:26:38,565">-som f&#248;lge av nedbrytelse av samfunnene.</p>
      <p end="01:26:42,160" begin="01:26:41,074">Fordi uten et samfunn-</p>
      <p end="01:26:44,824" begin="01:26:42,160">-f&#248;ler ingen av oss ansvarlige for noen andre.</p>
      <p end="01:26:46,526" begin="01:26:44,824">Vi er alle koblet sammen-</p>
      <p end="01:26:47,498" begin="01:26:46,526">-p&#229; mange plan.</p>
      <p end="01:26:49,466" begin="01:26:47,498">Hvis man er religi&#248;s-</p>
      <p end="01:26:51,641" begin="01:26:49,466">-forst&#229;r man det p&#229; et religi&#248;st plan.</p>
      <p end="01:26:55,457" begin="01:26:51,641">Men selv om man er praktisk, kan man se-</p>
      <p end="01:26:57,084" begin="01:26:55,457">-at vi er koblet sammen.</p>
      <p end="01:27:00,039" begin="01:26:57,084">Hvis jeg tramper i en s&#248;lepytt, og du st&#229;r ved siden av-</p>
      <p end="01:27:01,115" begin="01:27:00,039">-s&#229; skvetter det p&#229; deg.</p>
      <p end="01:27:05,423" begin="01:27:01,115">Hvis jeg skaper forurensning, da m&#229; du puste det inn.</p>
      <p end="01:27:06,593" begin="01:27:05,423">Hodet mitt vil si til meg-</p>
      <p end="01:27:09,720" begin="01:27:06,593">-at jeg er den eneste som er viktig.</p>
      <p end="01:27:13,323" begin="01:27:09,720">S&#229; jeg m&#229; l&#230;re meg selv gang p&#229; gang at det ikke er tilfellet.</p>
      <p end="01:27:18,036" begin="01:27:15,167">- [Kvinnelig gjest] N&#229;r du skrur p&#229; lyset, vil alt av lys skrus p&#229;?</p>
      <p end="01:27:19,300" begin="01:27:18,036">- Flesteparten. Jeg pr&#248;ver &#229;...</p>
      <p end="01:27:22,563" begin="01:27:19,300">- Okey, med det samme du gj&#248;r det, s&#229; sl&#229;s alt p&#229;.</p>
      <p end="01:27:24,925" begin="01:27:22,563">- Nei, nei, nei.<br/>Fordi jeg m&#229; sl&#229; p&#229; flere.</p>
      <p end="01:27:26,580" begin="01:27:24,925">Det er flere enn &#233;n bryter.</p>
      <p end="01:27:29,648" begin="01:27:26,580">- S&#229; du m&#229; sl&#229; p&#229; tre stykker-</p>
      <p end="01:27:30,892" begin="01:27:29,648">-og da vil de v&#230;re p&#229;.</p>
      <p end="01:27:31,585" begin="01:27:30,892">- Ja.</p>
      <p end="01:27:33,987" begin="01:27:31,585">- S&#229;, vi skal sl&#229; p&#229;... Okey.</p>
      <p end="01:27:36,349" begin="01:27:33,987">- Okey.</p>
      <p end="01:27:39,668" begin="01:27:36,349">- Det har ikke v&#230;rt et &#229;r siden-</p>
      <p end="01:27:43,349" begin="01:27:39,668">-fordi str&#248;ml&#248;sfasen startet i den sjette m&#229;neden.</p>
      <p end="01:27:45,631" begin="01:27:43,349">S&#229; det har v&#230;rt seks m&#229;neder siden vi har hatt str&#248;m.</p>
      <p end="01:27:50,622" begin="01:27:45,631">Det er takknemlighet for sm&#229; gleder.</p>
      <p end="01:27:52,262" begin="01:27:50,622">- Ohh...</p>
      <p end="01:27:54,989" begin="01:27:52,262">- Ja!</p>
      <p end="01:27:57,311" begin="01:27:54,989">[Isabella mumler]</p>
      <p end="01:28:04,253" begin="01:28:01,927">[Bl&#229;selyd]</p>
      <p end="01:28:07,677" begin="01:28:05,956">- Da er vi i gang.</p>
      <p end="01:28:16,949" begin="01:28:07,677">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="01:28:20,755" begin="01:28:16,949">- Jeg m&#229; si jeg var skeptisk i starten-</p>
      <p end="01:28:21,956" begin="01:28:20,755">-og jeg f&#248;lte at det var galskap-</p>
      <p end="01:28:27,305" begin="01:28:21,956">-og veldig dumt, og jeg hatet deg for det.</p>
      <p end="01:28:30,765" begin="01:28:27,305">Men jeg vil fortsette med syklingen.</p>
      <p end="01:28:34,502" begin="01:28:30,765">Jeg vil beholde s&#229; mye som vi kan. Ingen s&#248;ppel.</p>
      <p end="01:28:38,401" begin="01:28:34,502">Og jeg vil beholde markedet.</p>
      <p end="01:28:42,678" begin="01:28:38,401">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="01:28:46,953" begin="01:28:42,678">Jeg vil v&#230;re vegetarianer, men jeg vil ha en hotdog en gang i blant.</p>
      <p end="01:28:48,246" begin="01:28:46,953">[Colin humrer]</p>
      <p end="01:28:53,335" begin="01:28:48,246">Da ville jeg ha v&#230;rt en svinetarianer eller p&#248;lsetarianer.</p>
      <p end="01:28:57,779" begin="01:28:53,335">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
      <p end="01:29:02,201" begin="01:28:57,779">Jeg vil helst ikke ha TV i huset, men jeg kan ikke vente med &#229; g&#229; p&#229; kino.</p>
      <p end="01:29:04,306" begin="01:29:02,201">Og n&#229;r vi er p&#229; ferie, da er den p&#229;.</p>
      <p end="01:29:08,160" begin="01:29:06,163">Det er noen ting jeg har problemer med.</p>
      <p end="01:29:08,877" begin="01:29:08,160">- Ja.</p>
      <p end="01:29:10,640" begin="01:29:08,877">- Hvorfor kan vi ikke fjerne markene?</p>
      <p end="01:29:14,578" begin="01:29:10,640">Fordi de lager rabalder p&#229; kj&#248;kkenet.</p>
      <p end="01:29:18,325" begin="01:29:14,578">Og det kan v&#230;re en god del ting vi ikke kan gj&#248;re-</p>
      <p end="01:29:21,928" begin="01:29:18,325">-og det kan v&#230;re en av de tingene.</p>
      <p end="01:29:24,039" begin="01:29:21,928">Fordi jeg f&#229;r ta noen avgj&#248;relser her omkring.</p>
      <p end="01:29:28,039" begin="01:29:24,039">&#9834; [musikk] &#9834;</p>
